g%20victims%20of%20terrorism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar's%20remarks%20came%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20is%20an%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20and%20New%20Delhi%20abstained%20from%20a%20UN%20resolution%20that%20did%20not%20condemn%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks.%20He%20also%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20position%26quot%3B%20on%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20a%20good%20government%20and%20strong%20governance%20stand%20up%20for%20its%20people.%20Just%20as%20good%20governance%20is%20necessary%20at%20home%2C%20right%20judgements%20are%20necessary%20abroad.%20We%20take%20a%20strong%20position%20on%20terrorism%20because%20we%20are%20big%20victims%20of%20terrorism.%20We%20will%20have%20no%20credibility%20if%20we%20say%20that%20when%20terrorism%20impacts%20us%2C%20it's%20very%20serious%3B%20when%20it%20happens%20to%20somebody%20else%2C%20it's%20not%20serious.%20We%20need%20to%20have%20a%20consistent%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20while%20speaking%20at%20a%20Town%20hall%20in%20Bhopal%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20abstained%20from%20voting%20on%20the%20Jordanian%20resolution%20which%20called%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%2C%20durable%20and%20sustained%20humanitarian%20truce%26quot%3B%20between%20Israeli%20forces%20and%20Hamas%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20pertinent%20to%20note%20that%20India%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Canadian%20resolution%20which%20condemned%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Jordanian-led%20draft%20resolution%20was%20adopted%20by%20the%20General%20Assembly%2C%20with%20120%20votes%20in%20favour%2C%2014%20against%20and%2045%20abstentions.%20The%2045%20nations%20that%20abstained%20from%20voting%20on%20the%20resolution%20included%20Iceland%2C%20India%2C%20Panama%2C%20Lithuania%20and%20Greece.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20was%20adopted%20during%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly's%20emergency%20special%20session%20on%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20crisis.%20The%20UNGA%20also%20demanded%20%26quot%3Bcontinuous%2C%20sufficient%20and%20unhindered%26quot%3B%20provision%20of%20lifesaving%20supplies%20and%20services%20for%20civilians%20trapped%20inside%20the%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20expressing%20deep%20concerns%20over%20the%20deteriorating%20security%20situation%20and%20the%20astounding%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20India%20at%20the%20UN%20urged%20both%20parties%20to%20%26quot%3Bde-escalate%2C%20eschew%20violence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Deputy%20Permanent%20Representative%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20Yojna%20Patel%20on%20Friday%20(local%20time)%20in%20her%20remarks%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20(UNGA)%20Emergency%20Special%20Session%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20at%20the%20deteriorating%20security%20situation%20and%20the%20astounding%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%20The%20escalation%20of%20hostilities%20in%20the%20region%20will%20only%20exacerbate%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis.%20It%20is%20necessary%20for%20all%20parties%20to%20display%20the%20utmost%20responsibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20escalated%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%2C%20where%20about%202%2C500%20terrorists%20breached%20the%20border%20into%20Israel%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20leading%20to%20casualties%20and%20the%20seizure%20of%20hostages.%20Over%208%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20attacks%20since%20October%207.%20More%20than%201%2C400%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20EAM%20Jaishankar%20in%20Bhopal%20further%20highlighted%20how%20India's%20image%20has%20changed%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20how%20do%20you%20have%20a%20government%20that%20stands%20for%20what%20is%20necessary%20and%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20its%20people%3F%20A%20strong%20government%20and%20good%20government%20are%20two%20sides%20of%20one%20coin.%20In%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20India's%20image%20in%20the%20world%20has%20changed%20a%20lot.%20The%20way%20we%20handled%20the%20pandemic%20when%20developed%20nations%20were%20too%20stressful%3B%20as%20some%20had%20a%20totally%20collapsed%20public%20health%20response.%20We%20made%2C%20'Made%20in%20India'...'Invent%20in%20India'%20vaccine%2C%20we%20had%20a%20COWIN%20platform%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EAM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilarly%2C%20when%20every%20other%20country%20looks%20after%20the%20welfare%20of%20its%20people%20and%20its%20economic%20interests%2C%20the%20same%20countries%20in%20Europe%20are%20saying%20don't%20buy%20oil%20from%20Russia%3B%20they%20were%20themselves%20taking%20it%20and%20they%20made%20such%20a%20schedule%20that%20impacts%20their%20own%20population%20in%20the%20least%20possible%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20digital%20consumption%20of%20data%20in%20India%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20digital%20consumption%20of%20data%20in%20this%20country%20has%20doubled%20in%20the%20last%205%20years.%20Five%20years%20ago%2C%20for%20the%205G%20either%20you%20went%20to%20Europe%20or%20China.%20Europe%20was%20costly%20and%20China%2C%20you%20very%20well%20know...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20we%20have%20made%20our%20own%205G%20technology...Today%20we%20have%20fought%20covid%2C%20we%20deployed%205G%3B%20whatever%20has%20happened%20in%20last%20few%20weeks%2C%20the%20Chandrayan%20mission...it%20has%20left%20an%20impression%20on%20the%20entire%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20