0for%20Bollywood%3A%20he%20wants%20them%20to%20redo%20the%20superhit%20'Amar%20Akbar%20Anthony'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%2C%20born%20in%20London%20in%201970%20to%20parents%20who%20had%20arrived%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20explains%20why%20he%20believes%20that%20this%20is%20the%20right%20moment%20for%20such%20a%20request%20from%20a%20city%20like%20London%20which%20isn't%20unfamiliar%20to%20Bollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20Proposal%20to%20Bollywood.%20Please%20redo%20Amar%20Akbar%20Anthony%20in%20the%20UK%20because%20we%20have%20a%20Christian%20king%20(Ling%20Charles%20III)%2C%20a%20Muslim%20mayor%20(he%20himself)%20and%20a%20Hindu%20Prime%20Minister%20(Rishi%20Sunak)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20public%20housing%20with%20his%20six%20brothers%20and%20sister%20in%20Tooting%2C%20an%20ethnically%20diverse%20residential%20area%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20get%20to%20play%20Amitabh%20Bachchan's%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Mayor%20said%20with%20a%20chuckle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20featured%20Vinod%20Khanna%20(a%20Hindu%20police%20officer)%2C%20Rishi%20Kapoor%20(a%20Muslim%20qawwali%20singer)%20and%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20(Christian%20liquor%20seller).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLondon%20is%20the%20number%20one%20place%20for%20Bollywood%20films%20to%20be%20filmed%20and%20for%20people%20to%20come%20and%20invest%20in.%20I'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20Indians%20coming%20here%20as%20students%2C%20as%20tourists%2C%20as%20investors%2C%20and%20for%20locations%20for%20Bollywood%20movies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20Labour%20Party%20aged%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Khan%20regularly%20recalls%20how%20his%20father%20drove%20London's%20famous%20red%20buses%2C%20his%20mother%20was%20a%20seamstress%20and%20one%20of%20his%20brothers%20is%20a%20motor%20mechanic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20London%20is%20the%20greatest%20city%20in%20the%20world%20is%20because%20Indians%20have%20chosen%20to%20make%20it%20their%20home.%20These%20are%20Londoners%20who%20have%20gone%20on%20to%20become%20doctors%2C%20business%20people%2C%20politicians%2C%20chemists%2C%20pharmacists%2C%20scientists%2C%20journalists%20and%20so%20forth.%20Our%20diversity%20is%20a%20strength.%20London%20is%20a%20place%20where%20you%20can%20fulfil%20your%20potential.%20I%20call%20it%20the%20London%20Promise%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Khan%2C%20who%20made%20a%20name%20for%20himself%20as%20a%20vocal%20critic%20of%20Brexit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202005%20he%20gave%20up%20his%20legal%20career%20on%20becoming%20the%20member%20of%20parliament%20for%20Tooting%2C%20where%20he%20still%20lives%20with%20his%20lawyer%20wife%20Saadiya%20and%20their%20two%20daughters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698612000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F5ia4sq4o_sadiq-khan-1200_625x300_29_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-wants-bollywood-to-redo-amar-akbar-anthony-4526251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22London%20Mayor%20Sadiq%20Khan%2C%20gunning%20for%20a%20third%20term%2C%20has%20a%20request%20for%20Bollywood%3A%20he%20wants%20them%20to%20redo%20the%20superhit%20'Amar%20Akbar%20Anthony'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-wants-bollywood-to-redo-amar-akbar-anthony-4526251%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-wants-bollywood-to-redo-amar-akbar-anthony-4526251%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-london-mayor-sadiq-khan-wants-bollywood-to-redo-amar-akbar-anthony-4526251%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20calls%20on%20Pence%20for%20support%20after%20latter%20exits%202024%20race%22%2C%