ght%20and%20the%20GOP's%20sharply%20defined%20views%20on%20issues%20like%20abortion%2C%20many%20of%20those%20voters%20increasingly%20backed%20Democratic%20presidential%20nominees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225014%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mitch%20McConnell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653ea32d0487ff031cb19119%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223343%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20Mitch%20McConnell%20of%20Kentucky%20leads%20the%20GOP%20conference%20in%20the%20upper%20chamber.%3Cp%3EDrew%20Angerer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Foct%2F27%2Fmike-johnson-value-moral-conservative-republican%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantiabortion%20stance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20long-standing%20opposition%20to%20same-sex%20marriage%20were%20already%20known%20within%20the%20GOP%2C%20but%20his%20views%20are%20now%20fully%20on%20view%20on%20a%20national%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20might%20that%20impact%20the%20presidential%20race%2C%20as%20voters%20determine%20whether%20they'll%20continue%20to%20back%20a%20divided%20government%20or%20give%20one%20party%20full%20control%3F%20Could%20Johnson%20become%20a%20foil%2C%20similar%20to%20Clinton's%20needling%20of%20Gingrich%20ahead%20of%20the%201996%20presidential%20election%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20is%20nothing%20like%20the%20sort%20of%20bombastic%20figure%20that%20Gingrich%20was%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20but%20as%20the%20country%20has%20become%20more%20polarized%2C%20conservative%20priorities%20pushed%20by%20House%20Republicans%20could%20become%20an%20effective%20wedge%20for%20Democrats%20as%20they%20seek%20to%20hold%20the%20White%20House%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20South%20may%20decide%20control%20of%20the%20House%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20a%20221-212%20House%20majority%2C%20a%20razor-thin%20margin%20that%20empowered%20them%20earlier