weight%20carbon%20fibre%20and%20is%20just%20half%20a%20meter%20tall.%20The%20density%20of%20air%20on%20Mars%20in%20about%20one-hundredth%20of%20Earth's%20at%20sea%20level%2C%20or%20the%20density%20of%20air%20at%2027%2C000%20meters%20above%20earth%2C%20an%20altitude%20never%20reached%20by%20existing%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20fly%20Ingenuity%20the%20blades%20rotate%20at%202400%20and%202900%20rpm%2C%20or%20about%2010%20times%20faster%20than%20any%20helicopter%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIngenuity%20is%20an%20experiment%20of%20sorts%20to%20test%20powered%2C%20controlled%20flight%20on%20another%20world%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerched%20on%20the%20Perseverance%20rover%2C%20the%20chopper%20reached%20the%20surface%20of%20Mars%20like%20stowaway%20on%20February%2018%2C%202021.%20The%20Ingenuity%20helicopter%20was%20deployed%20to%20the%20surface%20on%20April%203%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20rover%20reached%20a%20suitable%20%26quot%3Bairfield%26quot%3B%20location%2C%20it%20released%20Ingenuity%20to%20the%20surface%20so%20it%20could%20perform%20a%20series%20of%20test%20flights%20over%20a%2030-Martian-day%20experimental%20window%20--%20similar%20to%20the%20India's%20Chandrayaan%20rover%20Pragyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia's%20historic%20moon%20mission%20received%20an%20emphatic%20thumbs-up%20from%20Dr%20Balaram.%20%26quot%3BVikram%20landing%20gave%20one%20goose%20bumps%2C%20ISRO%20should%20pursue%20its%20own%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20helicopter%20has%20completed%20its%20technology%20demonstration%20after%20three%20successful%20flights.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20first%20flight%20on%20April%2019%2C%202021%2C%20Ingenuity%20took%20off%2C%20climbed%20to%20about%203%20meters%20above%20the%20ground%2C%20hovered%20in%20the%20air%20briefly%2C%20completed%20a%20turn%2C%20and%20landed.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20major%20milestone%20having%20a%20powered%2C%20controlled%20flight%20in%20the%20extremely%20thin%20atmosphere%20of%20Mars.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20first%20flight%20in%20the%20world%20beyond%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20chopper%20successfully%20performed%20additional%20experimental%20flights%20of%20incrementally%20farther%20distance%20and%20greater%20altitude.%20So%20far%2C%20it%20has%20made%2064%20flights%20in%20the%20thin%20Martian%20atmosphere.%20Flying%20Ingenuity%20was%20truly%20the%20'Wright%20Brothers%20moment'%20on%20another%20planet%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarly%20next%20year%2C%20an%20Earth%20imaging%20satellite%20named%20NISAR%20--%20made%20jointly%20by%20India%20and%20the%20US%20--will%20be%20flown%20from%20Sriharikota.%20It%20would%20be%20part%20of%20the%20increasingly%20strong%20joint%20space%20initiative%20of%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20soft-spoken%20Dr%20Balaram%20says%20he%20is%20shortly%20retiring%20from%20NASA.%20Now%20he%20wants%20to%20help%20Indian%20students%20get%20attracted%20to%20the%20wonders%20of%20space%20and%20hopes%20to%20contribute%20more%20towards%20outreach%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20hands-on%20training%20at%20IIT%20Madras%20was%20instrumental%20in%20the%20success%20of%20flying%20Ingenuity.%20There%20are%20literally%20hundreds%20of%20students%20like%20him%20who%20can%20blossom%20and%20make%20India%20proud%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698601560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fnsia1da4_dr-j-bob-balaram_625x300_29_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflying-in-martian-sky-a-nasa-chopper-made-by-an-indian-4525965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20space%20agency%20NASA%20is%20flying%20an%20aircraft%20--%20a%20helicopter%20capable%20of%20flying%20in%20alien%20atmosphere%20--%20in%20Mars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflying-in-martian-sky