.businessinsider.com%2Fkanye-wests-turbulent-9-year-history-with-adidas-2022-11%232013-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20most%20lucrative%3C%2Fa%3E%20celebrity-fashion%20partnerships%20ever%20with%20Adidas%2C%20generating%20sales%20of%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20German%20sportswear%20brand%20eventually%20cut%20ties%20with%20Ye%20in%20October%202022%20after%20a%20series%20of%20public%20antisemitic%20tirades%20and%20offensive%20posts%20that%20caused%20him%20to%20be%20blocked%20from%20his%20social%20media%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20looked%20more%20closely%20into%20Ye's%20behavior%20that%20Adidas%20tolerated%20during%20the%20partnership%20by%20speaking%20to%20current%20and%20former%20employees%20of%20Adidas%20and%20Ye%2C%20and%20examining%20hundreds%20of%20previously%20undisclosed%20documents.%20The%20report%20concluded%20that%20the%20Yeezy%20partnership%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bfraught%20from%20the%20start.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20their%20first%20meeting%2C%20the%20report%20said%20that%20Ye%20was%20unhappy%20with%20the%20shoe%20designs%20and%20fabric%20samples%20presented.%20He%20drew%20a%20swastika%20on%20one%20of%20them%20to%20express%20his%20displeasure%2C%20according%20to%20two%20unnamed%20participants%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdidas%20is%20based%20in%20Germany%2C%20where%20most%20depictions%20of%20Nazi%20symbols%20are%20illegal%20and%20considered%20highly%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20detail%20of%20his%20troubling%20antisemitic%20behaviour%2C%20Ye%20told%20one%20Jewish%20manager%20at%20the%20company%20to%20kiss%20a%20picture%20of%20Hitler%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20concluded%20that%20the%20profits%20generated%20from%20sales%20of%20Yeezy%20merchandise%20let%20Adidas%20executives%20to%20tolerate%20Ye's%20erratic%20and%20offensive%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Ye%20has%20been%20less%20outspoken%