variety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fbox-office-five-nights-at-freddys-opening-weekend-shatters-expectations-1235772316%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fbox-office-five-nights-at-freddys-opening-weekend-shatters-expectations-1235772316%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20Built%20Dhamra%20LNG%20Terminal%20Entirely%20On%20Backing%20Of%20Promoters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20built%20an%20LNG%20import%20facility%20at%20Dhamra%20in%20Odisha%20entirely%20based%20on%20financial%20backing%20of%20promoters%2C%20with%20no%20financial%20undertaking%20or%20guarantees%20of%20public%20sector%20giants%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%2C%20who%20merely%20were%20tenants%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClarifying%20the%20group's%20position%2C%20they%20said%20Indian%20Oil%20Corporation%20(IOC)%20and%20GAIL%20(India)%20Ltd%20have%20hired%20capacity%20on%20the%20newly%20built%20terminal%20at%20rates%20lower%20than%20a%20similar%20but%20older%20and%20depreciated%20facility%20at%20Dahej%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20in%20response%20to%20reported%20comments%20by%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20who%20is%20facing%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%20examination%20over%20alleged%20'cash%20for%20query'%20in%20Parliament%2C%20on%20Dhamra%20being%20built%20on%20financial%20backing%20and%20commitments%20to%20buy%20gas%20at%20a%20fixed%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20cost%20of%20Dhamra%20LNG%20terminal%20is%20Rs%206%2C450%20crore%2C%20the%20sources%20said%20responding%20to%20Moitra's%20assertion%20that%20the%20terminal%20to%20import%20natural%20gas%20in%20its%20liquid%20form%2C%20called%20LNG%2C%20was%20built%20at%20a%20much%20higher%20cost%20than%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20that%20IOC%20incurred%20in%20construction%20of%20a%20similar%20sized%20facility%20at%20Ennore%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20no%20amount%20upfront%20or%20during%20the%20project%20either%20as%20cash%20or%20bank%20guarantee%20has%20been%20given%20by%20IOC%20and%20GAIL.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20fully%20financed%20by%20equity%20and%20debt%20by%20shareholders%20of%20Dhamra%20LNG%20terminal%2C%20they%20said%2C%20rejecting%20the%20assertion%20that%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20paid%20Rs%2046%2C500%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIOC%20had%20in%202015%20signed%20to%20use%20up%20to%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20terminal's%205%20million%20tonnes%20a%20year%20capacity%20for%20importing%20gas%20for%20its%20refineries%20at%20Haldia%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Paradip%20in%20Odisha.%20GAIL%20too%20had%20signed%20up%20for%201.5%20million%20tonnes%20of%20the%20terminal's%20regasification%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20asserted%20that%20its%20tariff%20and%20commercial%20terms%20of%20Dhamra%20LNG%20terminal%20(inclusive%20of%20port%20charges)%20was%20arrived%20at%20through%20competitive%20benchmarking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPetronet%20LNG%20(which%20is%20owned%20by%20IOC%2C%20GAIL%2C%20BPCL%20and%20ONGC)%20operates%20India's%20largest%20LNG%20terminal%20at%20Dahej%20was%20used%20as%20benchmarking%20the%20tariff%20and%20commercial%20terms%2C%20they%20said.%20Dhamra%20tariff%20is%201.5%20per%20cent%20lower%20(Rs%2046.49%20per%20ton%20or%20Rs%2021%20crore%20annually%20over%204.5%20million%20tonnes%20of%20LNG%20capacity%20use)%20than%20Dahej%20LNG%20terminal%20charges%20and%20has%20better%20commercial%20terms%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20had%2C%20however%2C%20compared%20the%20tariff%20of%20Dhamra%20with%20Ennore%2C%20which%20was%20commissioned%20not%20so%20long%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20charge%20compares%20to%20Rs%2057.38%20per%20mmBtu%20regasification%20charges%20for%20Ennore%20LNG%20terminal%2C%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOriginally%2C%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20had%20on%20September%2021%2C%202016%2C%20signed%20a%20'non-binding'%20agreement%20to%20buy%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Adani%20Group's%20Rs%205%2C500-crore%20Dhamra%20LNG%20project%20in%20Odisha.%20But%20that%20agreement%20expired%20on%20September%2020%2C%202018%2C%20without%20being%20translated%20into%20a%20firm%20pact%20apparently%20because%20of%20differences%20over%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20import%20LNG%20on%20their%20own%20and%20only%20pay%20tolling%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDhamra%20LNG%20will%20not%20buy%20and%20sell%20LNG%20during%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20facility.%20It%20only%20provides%20the%20service%20of%20LNG%20handling%20and%20dispatch%2C%20they%20said%2C%20rejecting%20the%20claim%20of%20a%2020-year%20fixed%20payment%20by%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20to%20Adani%20for%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20charge%20that%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20posed%20questions%20on%20Adani%20Group%20using%20Moitra's%20parliamentary%20logins%20as%20his%20business%20was%20impacted%20because%20of%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20committing%20to%20Dhamra%2C%20sources%20said%20Hiranandani's%20H-Energy%20had%20obtained%20a%20NOC%20from%20the%20Kolkata%20Port%20Trust%20to%20set%20up%20a%20LNG%20terminal%20in%20Kukrahati%20in%20February%202020.%20Though%20this%20NOC%20is%20still%20valid%2C%20they%20have%20been%20unsuccessful%20in%20progressing%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20terminal%20of%20H-Energy%20would%20cater%20to%20the%20same%20catchment%20area%20being%20serviced%20by%20Dhamra%20LNG%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EH-Energy%20was%20also%20looking%20at%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20to%20book%20capacity%20for%20their%20terminal.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20justify%20a%20value%20proposition%20to%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20that%20was%20better%20than%20what%20was%20being%20offered%20at%20Dhamra%20LNG%20terminal.%20This%20stymied%20their%20efforts%20to%20develop%20this%20facility%2C%20sources%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20not%20taking%20equity%20in%20Dhamra%2C%20they%20said%20the%20LNG%20terminal%20was%20able%20to%20offer%20commercially%20competitive%20terms%20to%20the%20users%20and%20given%20the%20pipeline%20tariff%20competitiveness%20of%20supplying%20nearby%20consumption%20centres%2C%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20were%20confident%20of%20bringing%20LNG%20at%20the%20cheapest%20terms%20via%20Dhamra%20to%20their%20consumption%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20their%20strategic%20objective%20was%20met%20without%20injecting%20equity%20and%20they%20decided%20to%20progress%20on%20a%20capacity%20booking%20basis%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20strong%20credentials%20of%20the%20project%20developers%20and%20the%20significant%20amount%20of%20pre-investment%20undertaken%20by%20Adani%20gave%20further%20confidence%20to%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%20on%20project%20completion%2C%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698591720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F2agnch4g_adani-group-logo-on-a-wall_625x300_08_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-group-built-dhamra-lng-terminal-entirely-on-backing-of-promoters-4525795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20built%20an%20LNG%20import%20facility%20at%20Dhamra%20in%20Odisha%20entirely%20based%20on%20financial%20backing%20of%20promoters%2C%20with%20no%20financial%20undertaking%20or%20guarantees%20of%20public%20sector%20giants%20IOC%20and%20GAIL%2C%20who%20merely%20were%20tenants%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-group-built-dhamra-lng-terminal-entirely-on-backing-of-promote