ar%20with%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20inside%20Rajahmundry%20Central%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20misappropriating%20funds%20from%20the%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20is%20currently%20lodged%20in%20the%20Rajahmundry%20Central%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20had%20reportedly%20said%20that%20with%20him%20in%20jail%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20possible%20for%20the%20leadership%20to%20campaign%20in%20Telangana%20and%20therefore%20the%20state%20party%20chief%20must%20explain%20to%20the%20cadre%20the%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20otherwise%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20showing%20keenness%20to%20go%20with%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20in%20Telangana%20while%20staying%20non-committal%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20on%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20that%20has%20declared%20that%20it%20will%20fight%20the%202024%20elections%20with%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%2C%20has%20put%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20an%20awkward%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Telugu%20Desam%20has%20had%20a%20support%20base%20in%20Telangana%20because%20of%20which%20it%20won%2015%20seats%20in%202014%20and%20two%20seats%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20elected%20MLAs%20subsequently%20shifted%20loyalty%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupporters%20of%20Mr%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20Telangana%20had%20been%20upset%20that%20the%20BRS%20had%20not%20given%20statements%20condemning%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20they%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20hold%20a%20protest%20in%20his%20support%20in%20the%20Hitech%20city%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20some%20groups%20said%20they%20would%20consider%20shifting%20their%20vote%20away%20from%20the%20BRS%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20that%20had%20the%20ruling%20party%20leadership%20worried%20and%20then%20multiple%20leaders%20spoke%20up%20condemning%20the%20manner%20of%20Mr%20Naidu's%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20BJP%20reaching%20out%20to%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20is%20significant.%20The%20Jana%20Sena%20has%20not%20been%20active%20in%20Telangana%20but%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20has%20a%20fan%20base.%20The%20BJP%20could%20hope%20that%20his%20announcement%20that%20he%20will%20fight%20the%20elections%20along%20with%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%2C%20could%20fetch%20them%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20Naidu%20supporters%20or%20at%20least%20move%20it%20away%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20BRS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20in%20Telangana%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20fighting%20to%20score%20a%20hat-trick%20in%20the%20state%2C%20is%20hoping%20people%20will%20go%20with%20%26quot%3BManchiga%20Chesindu%2C%20Malli%20Vasthadu%20(He%20did%20well%2C%20He%20will%20come%20back)%26quot%3B%20whereas%20the%20Opposition%20is%20hoping%20it%20will%20be%20%26quot%3B10%20samachralu%20ichcham.%20Marusdham%20(We%20gave%2010%20years.%20Let's%20Change)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR%20suddenly%20dissolved%20the%20assembly%20and%20announced%20his%20party%20candidates%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20taking%20competition%20by%20surprise.%20This%20time%20too%2C%20the%20BRS%20announced%20its%20candidates%20in%20August%20itself%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20off%20the%20blocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20has%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20his%20party%20would%20emerge%20victorious%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%2C%20securing%20between%2095%20and%20105%20seats%20in%20the%20119-member%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGoing%20all-out%2C%20the%20BJP%20promised%20to%20make%20a%20person%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20the%20party%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20previous%20Assembly%20election%20in%202018%2C%20the%20BRS%2C%20previously%20known%20as%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(TRS)%2C%20won%2088%20of%20the%20119%20seats%2C%20hogging%2047.4%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3