ers%26quot%3B%20during%20attempts%20to%20attack%20a%20village%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20such%20a%20slaughter%20going%20on%20there!%26quot%3B%20he%20says%20in%20the%20call%2C%20released%20by%20Ukraine's%20Military%20Intelligence%20Directorate%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kyivpost.com%2Fpost%2F23337%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Kyiv%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20noted%20that%20it%20could%20not%20verify%20the%20call's%20legitimacy.%20%26quot%3BMore%20than%20a%20thousand%20were%20killed%20there.%20The%20first%20and%20second%20battalion%20was%20thrown%20forward%20%E2%80%94-%20there's%20a%20hell%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20200s%2C%20even%20more%20300s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20using%20military%20code%20for%20dead%20and%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Soodavar%2C%20a%20researcher%20within%20the%20department%20of%20war%20studies%20at%20King's%20College%20London%2C%20recently%20wrote%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fukraine-russias-losses-mount-but-self-sacrifice-in-war-is-part-of-the-countrys-mythology-215235%5C%22%3Eself-sacrifice%20in%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20part%20of%20Russian%20mythology%20and%20that%20the%20death%20of%20a%20soldier%20was%20%26quot%3Bfor%20Russia%20a%20step%20toward%20achieving%20the%20fantasy%20of%20national%20prestige.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20trauma%20of%20military%20loss%20did%20not%20discourage%20Russians%20from%20fighting%20in%20Ukraine%20but%20was%20rather%20seen%20as%20a%20pathway%20to%20martyrdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDeath%20'washes%20away%20all%20the%20sins'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20soldiers%20march%20in%20unison%2C%20overseen%20by%20a%20senior%20military%20official.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a293796f7540cd06630af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20service%20members%20taking%20part%20in%20a%20military%20parade%20in%20Red%20Square%20on%20Victory%20Day%2C%20marking%20the%2078th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20victory%20over%20Nazi%20Germany%20in%20World%20War%20II.%3Cp%3EReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20Orthodox%20Christianity%20has%20been%20coopted%20to%20glorify%20and%20elevate%20a%20death%20in%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20official%20mantra%20of%20the%20Russian%20military%20is%20John%2015%3A13%2C%20from%20the%20Bible%2C%26quot%3B%20Carleton%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20essentially%20says%2C%20There%20is%20no%20greater%20love%20than%20to%20give%20one's%20life%20for%20one's%20brother.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20theme%20emerged%20strongly%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-orthodox-leader-dying-in-war-a-sacrifice-absolves-sins-2022-9%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomments%20by%20Patriarch%20Kirill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Russian%20Orthodox%20Church%2C%20in%20September%202022%2C%20in%20which%20he%20was%20encouraging%20Russian%20men%20to%20join%20up%20and%20be%20killed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20be%20free%20of%20sin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20person%20dies%20in%20the%20performance%20of%20this%20duty%2C%20then%20they%20have%20undoubtedly%20committed%20an%20act%20equivalent%20to%20sacrifice%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirill%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20have%20sacrificed%20themselves%20for%20others.%20And%20therefore%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20this%20sacrifice%20washes%20away%20all%20the%20sins%20that%20a%20person%20has%20committed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESchoolchildren%20are%20taught%20to%20embrace%20the%20myth%20of%20self-sacrifice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20posing%20for%20a%20photo%20while%20holding%20a%20Russian%20flag%20and%20a%20pitchfork%20in%20front%20of%20a%20destroyed%20Ukrainian%20rocket%20launcher%20system.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a2a2596f7540cd06630f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222430%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChildren%20pose%20on%20a%20destroyed%20Ukrainian%20Grad%20multiple%20rocket%20launcher%20system%20on%20public%20display%20at%20the%20central%20square%20in%20the%20occupied%20Ukrainian%20city%20of%20Donetsk.%3Cp%3EReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Carleton%20says%20that%20to%20retain%20the%20support%20of%20the%20public%2C%20Putin%20is%20more%20willing%20to%20dispatch%20certain%20Russians%20to%20the%20front%20lines%20than%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20war%20is%20being%20fought%20and%20bled%20by%20the%20marginalized%20communities%20socioeconomically%20speaking%20%E2%80%94%20and%20very%20often%20racially%20and%20ethnically%2C%26quot%3B%20Carleton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Putin%20recruiting%20soldiers%20from%20villages%20in%20remote%20parts%20of%20Russia%20and%20among%20its%20non-Russian%20ethnic%20groups%2C%20Putin%20can%20avoid%20the%20perception%20of%20high%20casualty%20rates.%20Carleton%20cited%20estimates%20that%20for%20every%20soldier%20from%20Moscow%20who%20is%20killed%2C%20%26quot%3Banother%20couple%20of%20hundred%20have%20died%20already%20in%20these%20villages.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20deaths%20are%20being%20spread%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Carleton%20said%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebut%20away%20from%20the%20major%20urban%20centers%2C%20because%20the%20major%20urban%20centers%20are%20where%20knowledge%20is%20disseminated%2C%26quot%3B%20Carleton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20pupils%20in%20Russian%20schools%20are%20being%20prepared%20to%20embrace%20self-sacrifice%20by%20Putin's%20government%2C%20according%20to%20Barbieri%2C%20who%20described%20Soviet-style%20patriotic%20indoctrination%20programs%20that%20she%20said%20have%20intensified%20since%20the%20war%20with%20Ukraine%20broke%20out