ernor-race-terry-mcauliffe-glenn-youngkin-biden-democrats-trump-2021-10%5C%22%3Estill%20had%20a%20purplish%20tinge%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20of%20Delegates%20flipping%20from%20Democratic%20control%20to%20the%20GOP%20that%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirginia-house-of-delegates-elections-live-results-updates-2021-11%5C%22%3Efurther%20bolstered%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20going%20for%20them%3A%20They%20have%20won%20every%20presidential%20election%20in%20Virginia%20since%20Barack%20Obama%20carried%20the%20state%20in%202008.%20Their%20strength%20in%20Northern%20Virginia%20and%20Hampton%20Roads%20%E2%80%94%20and%20increasingly%20in%20Richmond's%20suburbs%20%E2%80%94%20has%20often%20allowed%20them%20to%20offset%20the%20rural%20strength%20that%20Republicans%20enjoy.%20And%20most%20Virginia%20voters%20back%20some%20form%20of%20abortion%20rights%2C%20with%20a%20recent%20Washington%20Post-Schar%20School%20poll%20revealing%20that%2051%25%20of%20likely%20voters%20think%20Democrats%20are%20better%20suited%20to%20handle%20the%20issue%2C%20giving%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2023%2F10%2F20%2Fabortion-virginia-election-poll-youngkin-approval%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%2017-point%20edge%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20GOP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20uncertainty%20that%20comes%20with%20running%20in%20new%20districts%20across%20the%20state%2C%20Republicans%20believe%20it's%20a%20great%20opportunity%20for%20them%20to%20expand%20on%20their%20current%2048-46%20House%20of%20Delegates%20majority%20(with%20six%20vacancies)%20and%20win%20back%20the%20state%20Senate%2C%20where%20Democrats%20have%20a%2022-18%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225251%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Virginia%20state%20capitol%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F601f1a5a