quot%3B%20they%20reported%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Froyalsocietypublishing.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1098%2Frspa.1934.0077%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Proceedings%20of%20the%20Royal%20Society%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20sustaining%20a%20fusion%20experiment%20to%20generate%20continuous%20streams%20of%20energy%20is%20what%20scientists%20have%20been%20chasing%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20ways%20scientists%20control%20fusion%20reactions%20on%20Earth%20today%3A%20by%20forcing%20a%20capsule%20of%20fuel%20to%20implode%2C%20by%20using%20magnetic%20fields%20to%20confine%20plasma%2C%20or%20by%20combining%20the%20two%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fusion%20experiments%20at%20NIF%20use%20lasers%20for%20the%20implosion%20method.%20But%20the%20amount%20of%20energy%20needed%20to%20power%20the%20lasers%20has%20typically%20exceeded%20the%20energy%20the%20fusion%20reaction%20produces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20MUSE%20device%20at%20the%20PPPL%2C%20with%20a%20window%20showing%20a%20glowing%20red%20interior%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653182f596f7540cd060d50f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMUSE%2C%20a%20tabletop%20model%20under%20development%20at%20PPPL%2C%20which%20creates%20magnetic%20fields%20to%20control%20plasma.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Livingston%2C%20PPPL%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHurdle%202%3A%20Tritium%20is%20rare%20and%20expensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20the%20molecules%20hot%20enough%20to%20slam%20into%20each%20other%20and%20fuse%2C%20researchers%20form%20a%20plasma.%20It's%20a%20slurry%20of%20two%20hydrogen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foppenheimer-science-to-understand-physics-atomic-bombs-2023-7%5C%22%3Eisotopes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20deuterium%20and%20tritium.%20Only%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%2