Chandler%20Bing's%20funniest%20moments%20in%20Friends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698581896000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA416%2Fproduction%2F_131560024_p0gphhhx.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67252984%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20of%20Friends'%20funniest%20scenes%20relied%20on%20Chandler's%20quick%20wit%20or%20social%20awkwardness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2122%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fentertainment-arts-67252984%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Playing%20Cricket%20by%20the%20Gomti%3A%20The%20Lesser%20Known%20Story%20of%20the%20Game%20in%20UP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29174346%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-29-at-5.42.29-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELucknow%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20KD%20Singh%20%E2%80%98Babu%E2%80%99%20Stadium%20has%20hosted%20a%20solitary%20test%20match%2C%20an%20India%20versus%20Sri%20Lanka%20encounter%20in%201994.%20But%20both%20Anil%20Kumble%20and%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20made%20full%20use%20of%20their%20lone%20visit%20to%20the%20venue%20and%20made%20it%20an%20unforgettable%20one%20for%20different%20reasons%2C%20individually%20and%20team-wise.%20Tendulkar%20hammered%20his%20seventh%20Test%20century%20while%20leg-spinner%20Kumble%20bagged%20the%20first%20of%20his%20eight%20ten-wicket%20match%20hauls%20to%20steer%20India%20to%20an%20innings%20and%20119-run%20win%20in%20the%20first%20match%20of%20the%20three-test%20series.%20India%20also%20won%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20Ahmedabad%20to%20sweep%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Babu%E2%80%99%20stadium%2C%20named%20after%20the%20former%20India%20hockey%20captain%20and%20double%20Olympic%20gold%20medal%20winner%2C%20hosted%20just%20one%20more%20international%20encounter.%20It%20was%20a%20one-day%20international%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20a%20league%20game%20of%20the%20Nehru%20Cup%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20was%20a%20long%2C%2024-year%20lull%20before%20international%20cricket%20returned%20to%20the%20city%20in%202018%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20brand%20new%20and%20breath-taking%20Ekana%20Stadium.%20Since%20this%20modern%20venue%20has%20come%20up%2C%20the%20frequency%20of%20international%20matches%E2%80%99%20allotment%20to%20Lucknow%20has%20increased.%20So%20far%2C%20Ekana%20Stadium%20has%20hosted%20one%20test%2C%20seven%20ODIs%20(before%20the%20Indian-England%20World%20Cup%20match%20on%20October%2029)%20and%20six%20T20%20internationals%2C%20besides%20several%20IPL%20matches%20as%20it%20is%20also%20the%20home%20ground%20of%20the%20new%20franchise%2C%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kanpur%20has%20been%20the%20preferred%20choice%20for%20international%20matches%20since%201952%2C%20when%20it%20hosted%20its%20first%20test%20match%20at%20the%20Green%20Park%20Stadium.%20Despite%20the%20city%20not%20having%20the%20required%20quality%20facilities%20like%20five-star%20hotels%20for%20teams%20and%20air%20connectivity%20etc.%2C%20matches%20continued%20to%20be%20allotted%20to%20Kanpur%20as%20most%20of%20the%20officials%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20(UPCA)%20who%20had%20influence%20in%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20were%20based%20in%20the%20city%20and%20favoured%20the%20venue.%20Crucially%2C%20a%20Kanpur-based%20major%20business%20conglomerate%20has%20been%20heading%20the%20UPCA%20for%20years%20and%20backed%20these%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29174148%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-29-at-5.40.38-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29174148%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-29-at-5.40.38-PM.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29174148%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-29-at-5.40.38-PM-300x164.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29174148%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-29-at-5.40.38-PM-1024x558.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682387%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22589%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Ekana%20Stadium%20in%20Lucknow%20during%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Photo%3A%20Ekana.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20Kanpur%20having%20the%20sway%2C%20Lucknow%20hosted%20an%20international%20match%20very%20early%2C%20in%20the%20same%20year%20when%20Kanpur%20hosted%20its%20first%20test.%20That%20was%20the%20India-Pakistan%20test%20match%20in%201952%2C%20organised%20by%20a%20very%20influential%20individual%2C%20Habul%20Mukherjee%2C%20a%20renowned%20hockey%20coach%2C%20who%20was%20secretary%20of%20the%20now-defunct%20Lucknow%20Sports%20Association.%20The%20Lucknow-based%20Mukherjee%20wanted%20to%20promote%20hockey%20with%20the%20profit%20that%20he%20had%20expected%20to%20generate%20by%20hosting%20the%20cricket%20test.%20With%20that%20goal%20in%20mind%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20get%20the%20match%20allotted%20to%20Lucknow%2C%20despite%20there%20being%20no%20proper%20infrastructure%20to%20stage%20the%20important%20five-day%20encounter%20in%20the%20capital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20was%20played%20on%20a%20matting%20wicket%20laid%20out%20at%20the%20makeshift%20ground%2C%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20river%20Gomti%2C%20next%20to%20Lucknow%20University.%20At%20times%2C%20this%20venue%20is%20also%20called%20Gomti%20ground.%20Wooden%20poles%20and%20planks%20were%20erected%20and%20temporary%20seats%20were%20laid%20out%20for%20spectators%2C%20but%20most%20of%20them%20didn%E2%80%99t%20buy%20the%20tickets%20and%20the%20overall%20management%20was%20an%20utter%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELucknow-based%20Shahid%20Ali%20Khan%20Durrani%2C%20manager%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%E2%80%99s%20eventful%20tour%20of%20Australia%2FNew%20Zealand%2FFiji%20in%201980-81%2C%20was%20closely%20associated%20with%20Mukherjee%20and%20one%20of%20the%20volunteers%20during%20that%20Test.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20his%20wish%20to%20promote%20hockey%20from%20the%20profit%20he%20had%20hoped%20he%20would%20make%20from%20the%20Test%20match.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20disaster.%20He%20was%20left%20heartbroken%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2087-year-old%20former%20secretary%20of%20the%20Services%20Sports%20Control%20Board.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20recall%20a%20Commonwealth%20XI%2C%20captained%20by%20Sir%20Frank%20Worrell%2C%20visiting%20Lucknow%20in%201952.%20The%20match%20was%20played%20at%20the%20La%20Martiniere%20College%20ground.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22A%20Cricket%20Match%20in%20Bengal's%20Chinsurah%20and%20its%20Fascinating%20Connection%20to%20the%201857%20Revolt%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fa-cricket-match-in-bengals-chinsurah-and-its-fascinating-connection-to-the-1857-revolt%5C%22%3EA%20Cricket%20Match%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Chinsurah%20and%20its%20Fascinating%20Connection%20to%20the%201857%20Revolt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20all%20accounts%2C%20Lucknow%20never%20really%20made%20any%20serious%20efforts%20before%20or%20after%20that%20test%20to%20raise%20quality%20infrastructure%20so%20that%20it%20could%20host%20international%20cricket%20matches.%20Neeru%20Kapoor%2C%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Ranji%20Trophy%20players%2C%20attributes%20this%20to%20a%20lackadaisical%20attitude%20of%20successive%20generations%20of%20administrators%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20proper%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20years%20ago%20cricket%20was%20properly%20organised%20only%20at%20certain%20centres%2C%20like%20Allahabad%2C%20Bareilly%2C%20and%20Agra%20etc.%20It%20was%20very%20properly%20organised%20particularly%20in%20Allahabad%2C%20which%20has%20produced%20some%20great%20players%20like%20Anand%20Shukla%20and%20Mohamed%20Kaif.%20In%20Lucknow%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20infrastructure%20and%20no%20one%20to%20promote%20players%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%2080-year-old%20Kapoor%2C%20a%20former%20national%20women%E2%80%99s%20selector%2C%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThings%20are%20changing%20now%2C%20though.%20There%20are%2050-60%20cricket%20academies%20running%20in%20Lucknow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeats%20at%20Green%20Park%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Green%20Park%20had%20some%20serious%20shortcomings%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20fact%20that%20many%20great%20feats%20have%20been%20performed%20there.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20outstanding%20records%20has%20been%20legendary%20off-spinner%20Jasu%20Patel%E2%80%99s%2014-wicket%20match%20haul%20in%20a%20test%20match%20against%20Australia%20in%201959-60.%20He%20captured%20nine%20for%2069%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20and%20five%20for%2055%20in%20the%20second%20to%20spin%20India%20to%20119-run%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELeg-spinner%20Subhash%20Gupte%20also%20bagged%20nine%20wickets%20in%20an%20innings%20at%20this%20venue%20in%201958.%20In%20the%20West%20Indies%E2%80%99%20first%20innings%20of%20the%20second%20Test%2C%20he%20captured%20nine%20for%20102%2C%20though%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20prevent%20Gerry%20Alexander%E2%80%99s%20team%20from%20registering%20a%20203-run%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20at%20Green%20Park%20that%20Mohammed%20Azharuddin%20slammed%20his%20third%20consecutive%20century%20in%20his%20third%20test%20match%20%E2%80%93%20his%20third%20successive%20since%20making%20his%20debut%20against%20England%20in%201984-85.%20He%20also%20has%20the%20highest%20all-time%20average%20at%20this%20venue%20(181.00)%2C%20having%20tallied%20543%20runs%20in%20three%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoor%20on-field%20results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20belief%20that%20cricket%20administrators%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20have%20paid%20little%20attention%20to%20the%20on-field%20cricket%20and%20have%20done%20precious%20little%20over%20successive%20years%20and%20decades.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20its%20teams%E2%80%99%20performances%20have%20been%20poor%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20To%20mention%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20would%20suffice%20as%20an%20example%3A%20in%20the%2088%20years%20of%20the%20national%20championship%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20won%20the%20title%20only%20once%2C%20in%202005-06%20when%20Mohammed%20Kaif%20captained%20the%20team%2C%20and%20lost%20the%20finals%20on%20five%20other%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20has%20emerged%20champions%20in%20junior%20national%20tournaments%20a%20few%20times%2C%20but%20the%20promise%20shown%20has%20not%20translated%20into%20greater%20glory.%20Many%20of%20the%20players%20who%20shone%20in%20the%20junior%20ranks%20never%20lived%20up%20to%20their%20promise.%20Only%20a%20handful%20of%20them%20progressed%20to%20represent%20the%20country.%20So%2C%20it%20should%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20that%20since%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20UPCA%20in%201931%2C%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20players%20%E2%80%93%20Gopal%20Sharma%2C%20Rudra%20Pratap%20Singh%20(senior)%2C%20Gyanendra%20Pandey%2C%20Kaif%2C%20Piyush%20Chawla%2C%20Suresh%20Raina%2C%20Praveen%20Kumar%2C%20Bhuvneshwar%20Kumar%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Rudra%20Pratap%20Singh%20(junior)%2C%20and%20Sudeep%20Tyagi%20%E2%80%93%20have%20gone%20on%20to%20represent%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ahmedabad%20and%20the%20Art%20of%20Weaponising%20an%20India-Pakistan%20Spectacle%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fahmedabad-and-the-art-of-weaponising-an-india-pakistan-spectacle%5C%22%3EAhmedabad%20and%20the%20Art%20of%20Weaponising%20an%20India-Pakistan%20Spectacle%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20generally%20said%20that%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20state%20cricket%20administrators%20have%20two%20options%20when%20they%20represent%20the%20UPCA%20in%20the%20BCCI%3A%20seek%20positions%20for%20themselves%20in%20various%20committees%20of%20the%20Board%20or%20fight%20for%20players%20of%20their%20states.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20former%20seems%20true.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20the%20lone%20factor%20for%20the%20state%20not%20having%20produced%20players%20in%20ratio%20to%20its%20vast%20population.%20The%20perennial%20friction%20between%20Lucknow%20and%20Kanpur%20administrators%20has%20stunted%20players%E2%80%99%20progress%20as%20many%20genuinely%20talented%20cricketers%20have%20fallen%20by%20the%20wayside%20for%20want%20of%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDomination%20by%20Mumbai%20etc.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20also%20cite%20the%20domination%20of%20other%20powerful%20associations%2C%20saying%20their%20players%20got%20preferences%20over%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20cricketers%20over%20decades%20when%20it%20came%20to%20selection.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20total%20domination%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20players%20belonging%20to%20these%20associations.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20had%20abundant%20talent%2C%20but%20it%20has%20always%20been%20a%20question%20of%20getting%20the%20support%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20Players%20like%20Anand%20Shukla%2C%20Ubaid%20Kamal%20and%20Ashish%20Winston%20Zaidi%20never%20got%20sufficient%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20captain%20Ashok%20Bambi%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20corruption%20in%20selection%20of%20players%20for%20the%20various%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20teams%20makes%20news%20every%20season.%20A%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20an%20audio%20clip%2C%20in%20which%20someone%20could%20be%20heard%20purportedly%20demanding%20a%20few%20lakhs%20of%20rupees%20just%20for%20enabling%20a%20player%20to%20attend%20the%20trials%2C%20went%20viral.%20Apparently%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20investigation%20by%20the%20UPCA%20into%20this%2C%20or%20other%20such%20instances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20is%20the%20most%20populated%20state%20of%20India%20with%20over%2019%20crore%20people%2C%20and%20undoubtedly%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20talent.%20But%20the%20results%20are%20not%20commensurate%20with%20its%20population%20in%20terms%20of%20players%20representing%20the%20country%20and%20the%20state%20winning%20the%20national%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20changing%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20picture%20is%20changing%20now.%20Lucknow%20has%20been%20allotted%20five%20matches%20of%20the%20ongoing%20World%20Cup.%20Work%20on%20another%20stadium%20in%20Varanasi%20has%20begun%20and%20that%20will%20help%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20host%20a%20number%20of%20important%20matches%20in%20the%20future.%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Lucknow%20has%20gained%20a%20reputation%20as%20an%20international%20venue%20and%20it%20has%20culminated%20now%20in%20the%20city%20hosting%20the%20World%20Cup%20matches%2C%E2%80%9D%20Durrani%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20new%20cricket%20infrastructure%20coming%20up%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Ekana%20Stadium%20stands%20out.%20It%20is%20indeed%20a%20marvel%2C%20with%20easy%20viewing%20for%20spectators%20from%20all%20around%20the%20stadium%20as%20there%20are%20no%20pillars%20to%20pose%20obstruction%20to%20them.%20Hopefully%2C%20talented%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20players%20would%20also%20be%20selected%20without%20any%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQaiser%20Mohammad%20Ali%20has%20covered%20cricket%20for%20ov