3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbhumi-pednekar-our-society-is-conditioned-to-see-women-in-a-certain-way%2Farticleshow%2F104800786.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bahadur%20the%20Brave%20Shows%20How%20For%20Nepalese%20Migrant%20Workers%2C%20the%20Lockdown%20was%20Even%20More%20Difficult%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29164548%2FBahadur-the-Brave-2023_02-768x417-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20too%20long%20ago%2C%20the%20Nepali%20security%20guard%20was%20a%20ubiquitous%20figure%20in%20a%20city%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20almost%20every%20apartment%20complex%20employed%20a%20succession%20of%20men%20all%20called%20Bahadur.%20As%20if%20erasing%20their%20own%20identity%2C%20these%20Nepali%20men%2C%20when%20asked%20their%20name%2C%20invariably%20answered%20%E2%80%9CBahadur%E2%80%9D.%20They%20were%20hard-working%20and%20frugal%2C%20saving%20up%20their%20meagre%20earnings%20to%20take%20back%20to%20their%20families%20on%20their%20annual%C2%A0%20trip%20to%20their%20native%20villages%2C%20when%20they%20would%20be%20replaced%20by%20an%20incoming%20set%20of%20Bahadurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20more%20or%20less%20vanished%20from%20cities%20in%20western%20India%2C%20but%20in%20northern%20towns%20adjoining%20the%20Nepal%20border%2C%20they%20still%20come%20over%20for%20employment%20as%20casual%20labour%2C%20and%20it%20is%20this%20group%20of%20men%20that%20Diwa%20Shah%20has%20empathetically%20captured%20in%20her%20debut%20feature%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBahadur%20The%20Brave%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Set%20in%20Naintal%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20film%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20two%20Nepali%20friends%2C%20who%20have%20to%20make%20tough%20decisions%20about%20their%20future.%20The%20film%20won%20Shah%20the%20Kutxabank%20New%20Director%E2%80%99s%20Award%20at%20the%20San%20Sebastian%20Film%20Festival%20in%20Spain%20%E2%80%93%20a%20first%20for%20an%20Indian%20film%20%E2%80%93%20and%20is%20in%20competition%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Jio%20MAMI%20Film%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20follows%20the%20somewhat%20simple-minded%20Hansi%20(Rupesh%20Lama)%2C%20who%20does%20odd%20jobs%20of%20fetching%20and%20carrying%20loads%20like%20sacks%20of%20grain%20and%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20the%20neighbouring%20shopkeepers%20and%20homemakers.%20When%20the%20coronavirus%20strikes%20and%20a%20strict%20lockdown%20is%20imposed%20in%20the%20hill%20town%2C%20Hansi%20finds%20ways%20of%20dodging%20the%20curfew%2C%20and%20it%20hurts%20when%20he%20is%20fined%20Rs%20500%20by%20the%20cops%20for%20not%20wearing%20a%20mask%20%E2%80%93%20money%20he%20has%20just%20scraped%20together%20by%20haggling%20with%20his%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHansi%E2%80%99s%20buddy%20and%20brother-in-law%2C%20Dil%20Bahadur%20(Rahul%20Mukhia)%2C%20takes%20advantage%20of%20the%20shortage%20of%20labour%20by%20accepting%20construction%20jobs.%20The%20lockdown%20is%20tough%20on%20them%20as%20their%20roommates%20start%20going%20back%20to%20Nepal%20one%20by%20one%2C%20and%20the%20few%20that%20remain%20are%20forced%20to%20stay%20indoors%2C%20playing%20cards%20and%20taking%20turns%20cooking%20meals.%20Their%20already%20hard-scrabble%20existence%20is%20made%20more%20difficult%20by%20unexpectedly%20cruel%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHansi%20gets%20news%20that%20his%20son%20who%20needs%20surgery%20for%20a%20stomach%20ailment%20has%20fallen%20down%20and%20broken%20his%20arm.%20But%20he%20is%20ashamed%20to%20go%20home%20without%20money.%20Every%20time%20Dil%20Bahadur%20makes%20arrangements%20for%20him%20to%20return%2C%C2%A0%20Hansi%20finds%20excuses%20to%20miss%20the%20bus.%20For%20a%20man%20who%20has%20trouble%20following%20basic%20conversations%20(his%20interactions%20with%20a%20kind%20housewife%20are%20hilarious)%2C%20Hansi%20also%20has%20hidden%20reserves%20of%20sly%20resourcefulness%20%E2%80%93%20like%20persuading%20a%20cop%20to%20lie%20to%20Dil%20Bahadur%20about%20the%20expiry%20of%20his%20travel%20permit%20so%20that%20he%20can%20avoid%20getting%20on%20the%20bus%20to%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20impasse%20is%20automatically%20broken%20when%20Hansi%20and%20Dil%20Bahadur%20steal%20some%20liquor%20from%20a%20warehouse%20and%20are%20caught%20on%20the%20CCTV%20camera.%20The%20boss%20accuses%20Dil%20Bahadur%20of%20also%20stealing%20money%20and%20threatens%20to%20call%20the%20cops.%C2%A0Hansi%20uses%20this%20incident%20to%20persuade%20Dil%20Bahadur%20to%20go%20back%2C%20promising%20to%20follow.%20Inadvertently%2C%20this%20innocent%20ploy%20results%20in%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMemories%20of%20lockdown%20coverage%20in%20print%20and%20TV%20enumerated%20the%20deaths%20of%20Indian%20migrant%20workers%20trying%20desperately%20to%20reach%20their%20families.%20Poor%20Nepali%20migrants%2C%20who%20were%20not%20even%20citizens%20of%20India%2C%20were%20trapped%20when%20the%20border%20was%20sealed.%20Hostile%20locals%20shouted%20slogans%20to%20exhort%20the%20Nepal%20government%20to%20take%20their%20citizens%20back.%20The%20migrants%20had%20to%20camp%20out%20in%20the%20cold%20at%20the%20border%2C%20with%20no%20money%20and%20no%20access%20to%20food%20or%20supplies.%20The%20governments%20on%20either%20side%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20care%20less%20about%20these%20powerless%20men%2C%20who%20had%20nothing%20to%20offer%20in%20return%20for%20safe%20passage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDiwa%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20treatment%20of%20the%20subject%20is%20understated%20but%20also%20deeply%20humane.%20She%20portrays%20the%20bleakness%20of%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20migrants%20against%20a%20backdrop%20of%20scenic%20beauty.%20There%20is%20some%20humour%20and%20joy%20even%20in%20a%20crisis%20when%20the%20group%20of%20workers%20get%20together.%20But%20a%20desperate%20Hansi%20is%20left%20to%20stew%20in%20guilt%20and%20helplessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20lead%20actors%20bring%20out%20the%20truth%20and%20realism%20of%20the%20story%20with%20their%20performances%3B%20the%20viewer%20cannot%20but%20sympathise%20with%20the%20plight%20of%20these%20Bahadurs%20trying%20to%20keep%20their%20families%20out%20of%20abject%20poverty.%20The%20film%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20the%20famed%20resilience%20of%20the%20poor%20comes%20at%20a%20steep%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepa%20Gahlot%20is%20a%20national%20award%20winning%20critic%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698578731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29164548%2FBahadur-the-Brave-2023_02-768x417-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fbahadur-the-brave-shows-how-for-nepalese-migrant-workers-the-lockdown-was-even-more-difficult%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Debutante%20director%20Diwa%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20award-winning%20film%20showing%20at%20the%20Jio-MAMI%20festival%20is%20a%20sensitive%20look%20at%20their%20travails.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fbahadur-the-brave-shows-how-for-nepalese-migrant-workers-the-lockdown-was-even-more-difficult%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20Anti-Government%20Protests%20Turn%20Violent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29165242%2FF9f86ujbgAAN34J.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20police%20officer%20was%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20100%20people%20were%20injured%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbangladesh%2Ft-65210898%5C%22%3EBangladeshi%20capital%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20Dhaka%20on%20Saturday%20during%20protests%20demanding%20the%20resignation%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDemonstrators%20are%20also%20calling%20for%C2%A0free%20and%20fair%20elections%20under%20a%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20is%20due%20to%20hold%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbangladesh-can-eu-pressure-ensure-fair-elections%2Fa-66330225%5C%22%3Ea%20national%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20January%20next%20year%2C%20but%20the%20BNP%20is%20demanding%20Hasina%20to%20step%20down%20immediately.%20The%20ruling%20party%20maintains%20that%20the%20next%20general%20election%20must%20be%20overseen%20by%20the%20current%20government%20as%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Awami%20League%20party%20was%20accused%20of%20rigging%20the%20last%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpolls-close-in-bangladeshs-violence-marred-election%2Fa-46895204%5C%22%3Etwo%20elections%20in%202014%20and%202018%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20of%20cracking%20down%20on%20thousands%20of%20opposition%20activists%20during%20her%20nearly%2015-year%20rule%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHasina%2C%20who%20has%20maintained%20tight%20control%20since%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202009%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20authoritarianism%2C%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20cracking%20down%20on%20free%20speech%20and%20suppressing%20dissent%20while%20jailing%20her%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDozens%20injured%20in%20clashes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20fired%20tear%20gas%20and%20rubber%20bullets%20to%20disperse%20supporters%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbangladesh-what-has-happened-to-ex-pm-khaleda-zia%2Fa-66398142%5C%22%3Eopposition%20Bangladesh%20Nationalist%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(BNP)%20who%20gathered%20chanting%20anti-government%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20vehicles%2C%20including%20police%20vans%20and%20ambulances%2C%20were%20set%20on%20fire%2C%20according%20to%20police%20and%20media%20reports.%20Hundreds%20of%20opposition%20party%20activists%20were%20arrested%2C%20BNP%20leaders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDhaka%20Metropolitan%20Police%20spokesman%20Faruq%20Hossain%20said%20one%20police%20officer%20was%20killed%20and%2041%20others%20injured%20in%20clashes%20with%20protesters.%20Nine%20journalists%20were%20attacked%20and%20injured%20while%20trying%20to%20cover%20the%20clashes%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20opposition%20spokesman%2C%20Zahiruddin%20Swapan%2C%20said%20more%20than%201%20million%20activists%20joined%20their%20rally%2C%20but%20Hossain%20put%20the%20number%20at%20about%20200%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BNP%20has%20called%20for%20a%20day-long%20nationwide%20strike%20on%20Sunday.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20strike%20was%20called%20nationwide%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20attacks%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20police%20on%20the%20opposition%20activists%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20party%20spokesman%20Zahir%20Uddin%20Swapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolice%20and%20opposition%20trade%20blame%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20said%20the%20violence%20erupted%20when%20the%20opposition%20protesters%20attacked%20a%20bus%20carrying%20ruling%20Awami%20League%20activists.%20The%20activists%20were%20on%20their%20way%20to%20another%20rally%20organized%20by%20the%20party%20to%20counter%20the%20opposition%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20officer%20Harun-Or-Rashid%20said%20the%20BNP%20activists%20attacked%20members%20of%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20public%20establishments%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20vehicles%20without%20any%20provocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20supposed%20to%20conduct%20the%20rally%20peacefully%3B%20instead%2C%20they%20went%20on%20a%20rampage%20and%20caused%20harm%20to%20life%20and%20property%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20adding%20that%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20had%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20acts%20of%20sabotage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mirza%20Fakhrul%20Islam%20Alamgir%20accused%20security%20forces%20of%20ruining%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpeaceful%E2%80%9D%20rally.%20%E2%80%9COur%20rally%20was%20peaceful.%20But%20the%20authorities%20have%20used%20excessive%20force%20to%20ruin%20our%20rally.%20They%20attacked%20our%20people%20mercilessly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swapan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fbangladesh-anti-government-protests-turn-violent%2Fa-67244838%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698578618000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29165242%2FF9f86ujbgAAN34J.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-anti-government-protests-turn-violent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20violent%20clashes%20in%20Dhaka%20that%20left%20at%20least%20one%20person%20dead%2C%20Bangladesh's%20main%20opposition%20party%20called%20a%20nationwide%20strike%20for%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-anti-government-protests-turn-violent%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IRB%20Infrastructure%20Trust%20gets%20LoA%20for%20Rs%204%2C428%20crore%20project%20from%20NHAI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698577967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-09%2F25%2Ffull%2F1632515820-7505.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Firb-infrastructure-trust-gets-loa-for-rs-4-428-crore-project-from-nhai-123102900496_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20award%20takes%20the%20company's%20asset%20base%20to%20Rs%2075%2C000%20crore%2C%20IRB%20Infrastructure%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Firb-infrastructure-trust-gets-loa-for-rs-4-428-crore-project-from-n