.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20spokesperson%2C%20asked%20about%20Netanyahu's%20comments%20during%20a%20daily%20briefing%20with%20reporters%2C%20declined%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20surprise%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20the%20deadliest%20day%20of%20Israel's%2075-year%20history.%20Israel%20has%20since%20bombarded%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20with%20devastating%20air%20strikes%20and%20begun%20ground%20operations%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20toppling%20the%20Iran-backed%20Islamist%20group%20and%20returning%20scores%20of%20captives%20abducted%20from%20Israel%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20his%20Twitter%20(the%20former%20name%20for%20X)%20from%20overnight%2C%20which%20points%20to%20just%20one%20thing%3A%20he%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20security%2C%20he%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20hostages%2C%20only%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20opposition%20lawmaker%20Avigdor%20Lieberman%2C%20once%20Netanyahu's%20defense%20minister%2C%20in%20a%20radio%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYossi%20Cohen%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20Mossad%20spy%20agency%20under%20previous%20Netanyahu%20governments%2C%20told%20Israel%20Radio%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20take%20responsibility%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20your%20job%2C%20not%20from%20the%20middle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20took%20responsibility%20for%20the%20Mossad%2C%20for%20example%20...%20all%20that%20happened%2C%20from%20end%20to%20end%20was%20my%20responsibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698576600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F06g16ceg_benjamin-netanyahu_625x300_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fat-no-stage-time-warning-was-given-to-me-about-hamas-attack-israel-pm-4525238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli