%20Dutta%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20protesting%20villager%20Maya%20Nath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20worried%2C%20suddenly%20there%20might%20be%20a%20huge%20rush%20of%20water%2C%20we%20are%20keeping%20a%20constant%20watch%20on%20the%20river%2C%20we%20are%20not%20sending%20children%20to%20school%2C%20we%20have%20kept%20boats%20prepared%2C%20we%20are%20in%20panic%20mode%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20weeks%20after%20another%20disaster%20hit%20the%20Northeast%20-%20a%20dam%20breach%20in%20Sikkim%20following%20a%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20caused%20massive%20flash%20floods%20and%20several%20deaths.%20The%20landslide%20has%20alarmed%20the%20authorities%20in%20Assam's%20Lakhimpur%20district%2C%20downstream%20of%20the%20dam%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20dam%20at%20the%202%2C000%20megawatts%20lower%20Subansiri%20Hydropower%20project%20is%20one%20of%20the%20mega%20dams%20being%20developed%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20landslide%20blocked%20a%20diversion%20tunnel%20in%20the%20Subansiri%20river%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20drastic%20reduction%20in%20the%20downstream%20water%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20only%20diversion%20tunnel%20in%20use%20at%20the%20Subansiri%20Lower%20Hydroelectric%20Project%20as%20the%20other%20four%20diversion%20tunnels%20had%20already%20been%20blocked%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20National%20Hydroelectric%20Power%20Corporation%2C%20the%20mega%20dam%20developer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20We%20accept%20that%20we%20are%20facing%20some%20hurdles%20and%20now%20the%20focus%20is%20to%20close%20the%20gate%20of%20diversion%20tunnels%20so%20that%20landslides%20don't%20affect%20them%26quot%3B%20AN%20Mohammad%2C%20senior%20consultant%2C%20NHPC%2C%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20dam%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%2C%20asking%20people%20to%20restrain%20from%20activities%20like%20fishing%2C%20swimming%2C%20bathing%20and%20boating.%20People%20have%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20keep%20their%20cattle%20away%20from%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20landslides%20blocked%20four%20other%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20last%20year%2C%20the%20powerhouse%20protection%20wall%20collapsed%20due%20to%20tail%20race%20channel%20construction%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20project%20site%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20four%20major%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20incident%20has%20added%20to%20the%20growing%20concerns%20over%20mega%20dams%20on%20rivers%20in%20the%20eastern%20Himalayan%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20led%20by%20hydropower%20projects%20in%20the%20eastern%20Himalayas%20has%20once%20again%20raised%20the%20larger%20issue%20of%20how%20environmental%20risks%20are%20explored%20before%20developing%20hydropower%20projects.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20incident%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20where%20the%20dam%20got%20washed%20away%20due%20to%20a%20similar%20case%20of%20the%20lower%20Subansiri%20project%2C%20where%20for%20years%20people%20have%20raised%20concern%20about%20not%20only%20of%20downstream%20impact%20but%20also%20environmental%20risk%20factors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neeraj%20Vagholikar%2C%20a%20researcher%20on%20Environment%20and%20Hydropower.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESubansiri%2C%20being%20the%20largest%20tributary%20of%20the%20Bramhaputra%2C%20influences%20a%20larger%20ecosystem.%20If%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20restore%20the%20river%20flow%2C%20its%20impact%20could%20be%20wide-ranging.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698573360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fvdua7pq8_arunachal-dam-landslide_625x300_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-protests-in-assam-after-landslide-hits-mega-power-project-4525096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Massive%20protests%20have%20erupted%20in%20Ass