4%2Fmodi-thani.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20families%20of%20the%20eight%20Indian%20naval%20veterans%20sentenced%20to%20death%20by%20a%20Qatari%20court%20have%20appealed%20to%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20make%20a%20personal%20intervention%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20the%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2026%2C%20the%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance%20in%20Qatar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fqatar-eight-former-indian-navy-officers-handed-death-penalty%5C%22%3Esentenced%3C%2Fa%3E%20eight%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20officers%2C%20who%20had%20been%20working%20for%20a%20private%20company%2C%20to%20death.%20The%20Indian%20Ministry%20of%20External%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20judgment%20and%20was%20looking%20at%20all%20legal%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20against%20the%20eight%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20not%20been%20made%20public%2C%20but%20as%20per%20media%20reports%20they%20were%20detained%20on%20suspicion%20of%20passing%20down%20classified%20information%20to%20a%20third%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20sentencing%2C%20the%20sister%20of%20one%20of%20the%20former%20Indian%20navy%20officers%20made%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Indian%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20what%20we%20heard%20as%20my%20brother%2C%20Commander%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%2C%20who%20happens%20to%20be%20a%20decorated%20naval%20veteran%20has%20done%20no%20wrong%20and%20is%20innocent.%20We%20plead%20to%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20intervene%20and%20bring%20back%20our%20officers%2C%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%20Meetu%20Bhargava%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPurnendu%20Tiwari%20is%20also%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Pravasi%20Bharatiya%20Samman%20award%20for%20his%20contribution%20towards%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitte