20Delhi%20exhorted%20his%20church%20members%20this%20Sunday%20to%20pray%20for%20peace%20in%20Jerusalem%20(Psalm%20122%3A6)%20and%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20%E2%80%9CGod%E2%80%99s%20chosen%20people%E2%80%9D%20(Deuteronomy%207%3A6)%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Biblical%20commandment%20to%20Christians.%20Such%20calls%20are%20all%20too%20common%20whenever%20skirmishes%20break%20out%20between%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%2C%20which%20occur%20with%20chilling%20regularity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvangelical%20Christians%20around%20the%20globe%2C%20including%20this%20pastor%20in%20India%2C%20believe%20that%20Jews%20are%20%E2%80%9CGod%E2%80%99s%20chosen%20people%E2%80%9D%20who%20are%20under%20attack%20from%20their%20%E2%80%9Cenemies%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20religious%20obligation%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Christians%20to%20extend%20their%20unequivocal%20support%20to%20the%20state%20of%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20corollary%2C%20such%20a%20view%20holds%20Palestinians%20as%20%E2%80%98evil%E2%80%99%20(in%20the%20binary%20of%20good%20vs%20evil)%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20as%20the%20fulfilment%20of%20Biblical%20promises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPalestinians%20are%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%20and%20Jews%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20this%20perspective%20does%20is%20completely%20block%20out%20from%20public%20consciousness%20%E2%80%93%20either%20through%20design%20or%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20awareness%20%E2%80%93%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20Palestinian%20Jews%20and%20Christians%2C%20and%20Palestinians%20are%20not%20all%20Muslim.%20In%20fact%2C%20Jesus%20Christ%20himself%20was%20a%20Palestinian%20Jew%2C%20and%20most%20of%20the%20Biblical%20holy%20sites%20fall%20under%20present-day%20Palestine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20Evangelicals%2C%20however%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twn.my%2Ftitle2%2Fresurgence%2F2019%2F341-342%2Fhuman1.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplight%20of%20Palestinian%20Christians%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20does%20not%20cross%20their%20mind.%20Christians%20who%20constituted%20over%2010%25%20of%20Palestine%E2%80%99s%20population%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20establishment%20of%20Israel%20in%201948%20are%20now%20down%20to%202%25.%20It%20is%20most%20stark%20in%20Bethlehem%2C%20Jesus%E2%80%99s%20birthplace%2C%20as%20their%20share%20of%20the%20population%20has%20reduced%20from%2086%25%20to%20about%2010%25%20today.%20Like%20other%20Palestinians%2C%20they%20left%20their%20homeland%20as%20Israeli%20occupation%20increased.%20Even%20with%20their%20dipping%20numbers%2C%20Palestine%20still%20has%20a%20vibrant%20Christian%20community%20and%20the%20local%20church%20and%20its%20affiliate%20organisations%20are%20the%20biggest%20employers%20after%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28232437%2Fimage0-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28232437%2Fimage0-1.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28232437%2Fimage0-1-300x202.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682306%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22430%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChapel%20in%20Bethlehem%20where%20Yasser%20Arafat%20often%20offered%20prayers.%20Photo%3A%20File%2FThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20practising%20Christian%2C%20therefore%2C%20I%20see%20such%20calls%20for%20prayers%20in%20support%20of%20an%20apartheid%20regime%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20murderous%20campaign%20unleashed%20against%20Palestinians%20as%20morally%20reprehensible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20expose%20a%20lack%20of%20Biblical%20understanding%20and%20also%20spiritual%20bankruptcy.%20Many%20such%20Christians%20around%20the%20world%2C%20even%20in%20India%2C%20cherry-pick%20Biblical%20references%20to%20justify%20their%20support%20for%20Israel.%20Popular%20in%20such%20references%20is%20Genesis%2012%3A3%20verse%2C%20which%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20bless%20those%20who%20bless%20you%20%5BIsrael%5D%2C%20and%20whoever%20curses%20you%20I%20will%20curse%3B%20and%20all%20peoples%20on%20earth%20will%20be%20blessed%20through%20you.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEvangelical%20support%20for%20Zionism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoing%20beyond%20their%20vocal%20support%2C%20some%20evangelicals%20also%20aid%20Israel%20through%20generous%20contributions%20for%20its%20expansionist%20policies.%20The%20powerful%20American%20evangelical%20lobby%20in%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtontimes.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2Foct%2F9%2Fevangelical-christian-donations-help-fund-jewish-c%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epledged%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%245%20million%20immediate%20relief%20to%20Israel%2C%20following%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas.%20Many%20such%20organisations%2C%20particularly%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20even%20specifically%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2009%2F06%2F12%2F105310088%2Famerican-christian-funding-flows-to-jewish-settlers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eraise%20funds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20help%20Israel%20build%20settlements%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20which%20is%20outlawed%20by%20international%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJohn%20Hagee%2C%20an%20influential%20American%20evangelist%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPastorJohnHagee%2Fstatus%2F1712180816732717523%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Christians%20around%20the%20world%20to%20donate%20generously%2C%20promising%20that%20%E2%80%9C100%25%20funds%20raised%20will%20go%20to%20Israel%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20act%20in%20word%20and%20deed.%20Statements%20of%20support%20are%20welcome%2C%20but%2C%20on%20their%20own%2C%20they%20are%20insufficient.%20Love%20is%20not%20what%20you%20say.%20Love%20is%20what%20you%20do.%20Join%20us%20in%20this%20fight%2C%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20deliverance%20will%20come.%20But%2C%20if%20we%20do%20nothing%2C%20it%20is%20we%20who%20perish%E2%80%A6%20Join%20us%20today%20in%20this%20righteous%20fight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hagee%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement%2C%20right%20after%20the%20surprise%20attack%20by%20Hamas.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHagee%2C%20who%20claims%20to%20have%2010%20million%20followers%2C%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Christians%20United%20for%20Israel%20(CUFI)%2C%20the%20largest%20pro-Israel%20American%20organisation.%20CUFI%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20powerful%20American%20evangelical%20lobby%20and%20whose%20connections%20reach%20the%20US%20Congress%20and%20White%20House%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcufi.org%2Fpress-releases%2Fcufi-statement-on-hamas-attack%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evowed%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cconfront%20and%20overcome%20any%20elected%20official%20in%20Washington%20who%20would%20try%20to%20undermine%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20defend%20herself%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fby-fully-supporting-israel-the-west-has-chosen-to-forget-the-suffering-of-palestinians%5C%22%3EBy%20Fully%20Supporting%20Israel%2C%20the%20West%20Has%20Chosen%20to%20Forget%20the%20Suffering%20of%20Palestinians%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20likes%20of%20well-known%20theologists%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchristianitytoday.com%2Fct%2F2023%2Foctober-web-only%2Fisrael-hamas-russell-moore-moral-terrorist.html%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dpost%26utm_campaign%3Darticle%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERussell%20Moore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20say%20%E2%80%9Can%20Israeli%20life%20is%20of%20no%20more%20value%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20God%20than%20a%20Palestinian%20life%2C%20and%20vice%20versa%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20feel-good%20morality%20%E2%80%93%20they%20also%20marshal%20%E2%80%98evidence%E2%80%99%20through%20their%20selective%20reading%20of%20the%20Bible%20to%20advance%20the%20same%20%E2%80%98God%E2%80%99s%20chosen%20people%E2%80%99%20trope.%20%E2%80%9COur%20Lord%20Jesus%20was%20and%20is%20a%20Jewish%20man%20from%20Galilee.%20Rage%20against%20the%20Jewish%20people%20is%20rage%20against%20him%2C%20and%2C%20because%20we%20are%20in%20him%2C%20against%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.christianitytoday.com%2Fct%2F2023%2Foctober-web-only%2Fisrael-hamas-middle-east-war-christians.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Russell%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20October%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMounting%20pressure%20on%20the%20political%20class%20in%20the%20US%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20not%20all%20Christians%20subscribe%20to%20such%20a%20view%2C%20but%20evangelical%20Christians%2C%20whose%20numbers%20have%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20around%20the%20world%2C%20avowedly%20believe%20and%20support%20such%20thinking.%20Resourceful%20and%20well-organised%20American%20evangelicals%20not%20only%20limit%20their%20beliefs%20to%20the%20spiritual%20realm%20but%20also%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20political%20class%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20US%20maintains%20a%20favourable%20policy%20towards%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20problematic%20line%20of%20thinking%20is%20actually%20grounded%20in%20the%20dangerous%20intermixing%20of%20a%20Christian%20theological%20framework%20called%20%E2%80%98Dispensational%20Premillennialism%E2%80%99%20and%20theopolitical%20ideology%20of%20%E2%80%98Christian%20Zionism%E2%80%99.%20Together%2C%20they%20misguide%20Christians%20in%20favour%20of%20Israel%2C%20away%20from%20the%20fundamental%20tenet%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%E2%80%99s%20teaching%2C%20which%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthou%20shalt%20love%20thy%20neighbour%20as%20thyself%E2%80%9D%20(Mark%2012%3A31).%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20other%20theological%20frameworks%20which%20see%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20for%20what%20it%20is%20%E2%80%93%20as%20an%20issue%20of%20nationhood%2C%20dispossession%2C%20and%20occupation%20%E2%80%93%20however%2C%20they%20get%20drowned%20out%20in%20this%20particular%20discourse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29142717%2F16035181719_2bbd22fd2c_k.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29142717%2F16035181719_2bbd22fd2c_k.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29142717%2F16035181719_2bbd22fd2c_k-300x216.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29142717%2F16035181719_2bbd22fd2c_k-1024x736.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682356%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22863%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESeries%20of%20maps%20showing%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20of%20Palestine.%20Photo%3A%20Flickr.com%2F%20Palestine%20Solidarity%20Campaign%2FCC%20BY%202.0%20DEED.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDispensational%20premillennialism%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDispensationalism%20holds%20the%20view%20that%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%20is%20divided%20into%20various%20dispensations%20(periods).%20In%20each%20of%20these%20distinctive%20dispensations%2C%20God%20relates%20to%20mankind%20and%20the%20world%20in%20a%20different%20way.%20There%20are%20seven%20dispensations%20according%20to%20dispensationalists%2C%20and%20the%20world%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20sixth%20dispensation.%20The%20present%20dispensation%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Church%20age%E2%80%99%20is%20marked%20by%20the%20unlimited%20Grace%20of%20God%20and%20is%20moving%20towards%20the%20final%20millennium%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world%20and%20Judgement%20Day.%20The%20Church%20age%20is%20also%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.lse.ac.uk%2Freligionglobalsociety%2F2021%2F08%2Fpraying-for-the-peace-of-jerusalem-an-introduction-to-american-christian-zionism%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eage%20of%20downward%20spiral%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20bringing%20with%20it%20more%20immorality%2C%20apostasy%2C%20poverty%2C%20war%2C%20and%20natural%20disaster.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20world%20moves%20closer%20to%20the%20end%20of%20this%20dispensation%2C%20Jews%20are%20said%20to%20return%20from%20around%20the%20world%20to%20their%20promised%20land%20of%20Israel%20(Zechariah%2012%3A10%2C%2013%3A1%20and%20Ezekial%2036%3A24).%20After%20a%20seven-year%20Great%20Tribulation%20for%20the%20world%20under%20Anti-Christ%2C%20this%20dispensation%20will%20culminate%20with%20the%20Battle%20of%20Armageddon%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20present-day%20Israel%20in%20which%20Jesus%20defeats%20the%20evil%20armies%20who%20stood%20against%20Israel.%20Only%20those%20Jews%20who%20accept%20Jesus%20as%20their%20spiritual%20and%20political%20authority%20remains%20after%20the%20Great%20Tribulation%20and%20others%20will%20perish.%20A%20theocratic%20and%20just%20kingdom%20is%20then%20established%20under%20Jesus%20as%20a%20military%20conqueror%2C%20who%20will%20reign%20for%20a%20millennium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28232644%2F1024px-Holy_Land_2016_P0657_Jerusalem_view_from_Mount_of_Olives.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28232644%2F1024px-Holy_Land_2016_P0657_Jerusalem_view_from_Mount_of_Olives.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28232644%2F1024px-Holy_Land_2016_P0657_Jerusalem_view_from_Mount_of_Olives-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682307%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJerusalem%20view%20from%20Mount%20of%20Olives.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FFallaner%2FCC%20BY-SA%204.0%20DEED.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEschatology%2C%20a%20branch%20of%20Christian%20religious%20studies%2C%20deals%20with%20the%20End%20of%20the%20World%2C%20Judgement%20Day%2C%20and%20Jesus%20Christ%E2%80%99s%20Second%20Coming.%20And%20according%20to%20the%20Christian%20eschatology%20of%20the%20dispensationalist%20strand%2C%20Jews%20thus%20play%20a%20seminal%20role%20in%20the%20fulfillment%20of%20prophecies%20relating%20to%20the%20End%20Times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20establishment%20of%20Israel%20in%201948%2C%20the%20capturing%20of%20Jerusalem%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%20in%20the%20Six-Day%20War%20of%201967%2C%20the%20emergence%20of%20Israel%20as%20a%20powerful%20military%20power%2C%20and%20more%20recently%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20US%20embassy%20in%20Jerusalem%20are%20seen%20as%20the%20fulfilment%20of%20%E2%80%98End%20Times%E2%80%99%20prophecies%20foretold%20by%20the%20Bible.%20The%20rebuilding%20of%20a%20Jewish%20holy%20place%20on%20the%20Temple%20Mount%2C%20where%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%20currently%20stands%2C%20and%20future%20control%20of%20all%20of%20Palestine%20by%20Israel%20are%20prophecies%20which%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20fulfilled.%20Jews%2C%20therefore%2C%20are%20mere%20pawns%20without%20any%20agency%20for%20dispensationalist%20Christians%20who%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20realisation%20of%20End%20Time%20prophecies.%20All%20this%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20nothing%20but%20a%20clear%20case%20of%20anti-Semitism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dispensationalist%20line%20of%20thinking%20is%20based%20on%20a%20literal%20reading%20of%20the%20Bible%2C%20in%20particular%20one%20passage%20from%20the%20Bible%20(Revelation%2020)%2C%20which%20talks%20about%20the%20apocalyptic%20end%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20Great%20Tribulation%2C%20and%20Jesus%20Christ%E2%80%99s%20Second%20Coming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20reading%20of%20the%20Bible%20and%20the%20centrality%20of%20Jews%20to%20God%E2%80%99s%20plan%2C%20as%20it%20were%2C%20was%20first%20systematised%20by%20a%2019th%20Century%20Anglo-Irish%20Bible%20teacher%2C%20John%20Nelson%20Darby%2C%20who%20is%20regarded%20as%20the%20Father%20of%20Dispensationalism.%20With%20this%20theological%20framework%20gaining%20ground%20across%20the%20transatlantic%20in%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20the%20emerging%20Christian%20Right%20in%20the%20US%20made%20it%20a%20key%20part%20of%20their%20political%20engagement.%20The%20establishment%20of%20theological%20centres%20and%20Bible%20institutes%20and%20seminaries%20in%20the%2020th%20century%20helped%20in%20popularising%20dispensationalism.%20Hal%20Lindsey%E2%80%99s%20popular%20book%20among%20American%20Christians%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Late%20Great%20Earth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20published%20in%20the%201970s%20also%20added%20pace%20to%20its%20spread.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20this%20theological%20framework%20as%20the%20basis%2C%20a%20rising%20number%20of%20evangelical%20Christians%20in%20the%20US%2C%20from%20the%201970s%2C%20have%20begun%20to%20rally%20behind%20the%20Zionist%20movement%20for%20a%20Jewish%20homeland%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20a%20marked%20difference%20from%20the%20previous%20generation%20of%20Christians%20who%20had%20actually%20viewed%20Jews%20as%20%E2%80%9CChrist%20killers%E2%80%9D%20and%20were%20known%20for%20their%20antisemitic%20views.%20In%20the%20following%20decades%20since%2C%20Christian%20Zionism%20has%20thus%20emerged%20as%20a%20strong%20movement%2C%20with%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20supporters%20and%20more%20than%20adequate%20resources%20at%20its%20disposal.%20American%20Christian%20Zionist%20organisations%20which%20began%20to%20mushroom%20in%20the%20subsequent%20decades%20mobilised%20followers%20through%20large-scale%20conventions%20and%20Holy%20Land%20tours%2C%20consolidating%20them%20as%20a%20strong%20political%20lobby.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-war-on-palestinians-language-in-the-service-of-the-unspeakable%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20War%20on%20Palestinians%3A%20Language%20in%20the%20Service%20of%20the%20Unspeakable%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChristian%20Zionism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20began%20as%20a%20fledgling%20and%20diffused%20movement%20following%20the%20establishment%20of%20Israel%20in%201948%2C%20Christian%20Zionism%20emerged%20powerfully%20on%20the%20political%20scene%20as%20an%20organised%20movement%20by%20the%201970s.%20By%20then%2C%20the%20debates%20and%20theological%20wrangling%20around%20the%20role%20of%20Israel%20and%20the%20significance%20of%20Jews%2C%20according%20to%20Christian%20eschatology%2C%20had%20settled%2C%20giving%20Christian%20Zionism%20a%20clear-cut%20mission%20and%20vision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBuilding%20on%20the%20work%20of%20influential%20American%20preachers%20like%20D.L.%20Moody%20in%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20a%20number%20of%20high-profile%20American%20evangelists%20and%20Bible%20teachers%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20like%20Billy%20Graham%2C%20G.%20Douglas%20Young%2C%20John%20Hagee%2C%20Arnold%20T.%20Olson%2C%20Jerry%20Falwell%20Sr.%2C%20Pat%20Robertson%2C%20Hal%20Lindsey%2C%20among%20others%20further%20helped%20in%20its%20spread.%20Some%20of%20them%20even%20served%20as%20advisors%20and%20counsellors%20to%20US%20presidents.%20For%20instance%2C%20Falwell%2C%20Robertson%2C%20and%20Lindsey%20were%20part%20of%20many%20of%20the%20official%20programmes%20held%20at%20the%20White%20House%20during%20Ronald%20Reagn%E2%80%99s%20era.%20Even%20Martin%20Luther%20King%20Jr.%20was%20one%20of%20the%20staunchest%20supporters%20of%20Israel%20and%20Christian%20Zionism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20all%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.christianitytoday.com%2Fct%2F2023%2Foctober-web-only%2Fisrael-hamas-war-palestine-evangelical-christian-zionism.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBilly%20Graham%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20a%20towering%20figure%20in%20the%20American%20evangelical%20firmament%20and%20whose%20%E2%80%98crusades%E2%80%99%20were%20attended%20by%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cproverbial%20sun%20around%20which%20much%20of%20postwar%20evangelical-Jewish%20relations%20orbited%E2%80%9D.%20As%20someone%20who%20is%20said%20to%20have%20known%20every%20US%20president%20from%20Harry%20Truman%20to%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20Graham%20used%20his%20clout%20to%20garner%20support%20for%20the%20Zionist%20cause.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28233630%2FFotoJet.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28233630%2FFotoJet.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28233630%2FFotoJet-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28233630%2FFotoJet-1024x459.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682309%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22538%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBilly%20Graham%20with%20US%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan%20(left).%20Billy%20Graham%20with%20US%20President%20Barack%20Obama.%20Photos%3A%20Graham%20with%20Reagan%20(Wikimedia%20Commons%2FWhite%20House%20Photographic%20Collection%2FCC0%201.0%20DEED)%2C%20and%20Graham%20with%20Obama%20(Wikimedia%20Commons%2FThe%20White%20House%2FCC0%201.0%20DEED).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20believe%20that%20it%20was%20Graham%20who%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20background%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fview%2Farticles%2F2018-02-26%2Fbilly-graham-made-israel-ok-with-evangelicals%3Fembedded-checkout%3Dtrue%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epersuading%20President%20Nixon%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20airlift%20the%20largest%20amount%20of%20aid%20in%20US%20history%20to%20send%20enormous%20shipments%20of%20tanks%2C%20jet%20fighters%2C%20and%20ammunition%20to%20help%20Israel%20in%20the%201973%20Yom%20Kippur%20War.%20In%20the%20initial%20days%20of%20that%20war%2C%20it%20seemed%20the%20young%20Jewish%20state%20would%20not%20survive%20the%20double-front%20war%20launched%20by%20Egypt%20and%20Syria%20but%20for%20the%20support%20from%20the%20US.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EStrategic%20interests%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20then%2C%20the%20increasing%20realisation%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20US%20political%20establishment%20to%20have%20a%20trusted%20ally%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Israel%20in%20a%20strategic%20and%20resource-rich%20region%20also%20helped%20Christian%20Zionists%20to%20advance%20their%20cause.%20Christian%20Zionists%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20taking%20its%20message%20through%20popular%20phrases%20like%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20land%20without%20a%20people%20for%20a%20people%20without%20a%20land.%E2%80%9D%20What%20such%20messaging%20had%20done%20is%20to%20present%20Palestine%20as%20an%20uninhabited%20land%20and%20Jews%20just%20came%20over%20to%20settle%20down%20there%20in%201948%20to%20escape%20persecution%20in%20Europe.%20However%2C%20what%20Christian%20Zionists%20either%20fail%20to%20realise%20or%20purposely%20deny%20is%20that%20diverse%20groups%20of%20Arab%20Muslims%2C%20Jews%2C%20and%20Christians%20had%20been%20living%20in%20historic%20Palestine%20for%20centuries%20when%20Israel%20was%20established%20by%20the%20fiat%20of%20Western%20powers%20in%201948.%20However%2C%20such%20historical%20realities%20pale%20in%20front%20of%20propaganda%20by%20both%20Jewish%20and%20Christian%20Zionists.%20Today%2C%20support%20for%20Israel%20in%20the%20US%20is%20bipartisan%2C%20which%20is%20clearly%20reflected%20in%20its%20foreign%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202017%2C%20when%20the%20US%20moved%20its%20embassy%20in%20Israel%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20Jerusalem%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20openly%20declared%20that%20it%20was%20done%20for%20Christian%20evangelists.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20moved%20the%20capital%20of%20Israel%20to%20Jerusalem.%20That%E2%80%99s%20for%20the%20evangelicals.%20You%20know%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20amazing%20with%20that%20%E2%80%94%20the%20evangelicals%20are%20more%20excited%20by%20that%20than%20Jewish%20people.%20That%E2%80%99s%20right%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20incredible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Trump%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Ftrump-says-he-moved-us-embassy-to-jerusalem-for-the-evangelicals%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannounced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20August%202018.%20Although%20Israel%20considers%20Jerusalem%20as%20its%20capital%2C%20the%20world%2C%20however%2C%20treats%20it%20as%20an%20international%20city%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20Partition%20Plan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2023%2F08%2F21%2Fhow-americans-view-israel-netanyahu-and-u-s-israel-relations-in-5-charts%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecent%20Pew%20Survey%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%2055%25%20of%20the%20US%20citizens%20view%20Israel%20favourably%2C%20of%20whom%2080%25%20are%20white%20evangelicals%2C%2061%25%20white%20non-evangelicals%2C%20and%2043%25%20Black%20Protestants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20such%20wide%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20it%20would%20be%20risky%20for%20any%20political%20party%20or%20leader%20in%20the%20US%20to%20call%20out%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%20and%20lend%20genuine%20vocal%20support%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0even%20if%20such%20an%20intention%20existed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20All%20the%20declarations%20about%20the%20two-state%20solution%20are%20mere%20lip%20service.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAn%20alternative%20theological%20discourse%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20Christians%20around%20the%20world%20who%20do%20not%20subscribe%20to%20the%20exclusivist%20and%20oppressive%20views%20of%20dispensationalism%20and%20Christian%20Zionism.%20Numerous%20Biblical%20verses%20point%20out%20that%20the%20Biblical%20God%20does%20not%20delight%20in%20the%20death%20and%20destruction%20of%20Palestine%20people%2C%20or%20any%20other%20ethnic%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Romans%2010%3A12%2C%20it%20is%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20difference%20between%20Jew%20and%20Gentile.%E2%80%9D%20Similarly%2C%201%20Peter%202%3A9-10%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20you%20are%20a%20chosen%20people%2C%20a%20royal%20priesthood%2C%20a%20holy%20nation%2C%20God%E2%80%99s%20special%20possession%2C%20that%20you%20may%20declare%20the%20praises%20of%20him%20who%20called%20you%20out%20of%20darkness%20into%20his%20wonderful%20light.%20Once%20you%20were%20not%20a%20people%2C%20but%20now%20you%20are%20the%20people%20of%20God%3B%20once%20you%20had%20not%20received%20mercy%2C%20but%20now%20you%20have%20received%20mercy.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20particular%20verse%20by%20Apostle%20Peter%20emphasises%20that%20everyone%20who%20believes%20in%20Christ%20has%20become%20part%20of%20God%E2%80%99s%20chosen%20people.%20Numerous%20other%20verses%20from%20the%20Bible%20debunk%20the%20assertions%20of%20dispensationalism%20and%20Christian%20Zionism%20(Exodus%2019%3A5%2C6%2C%20Ephesians%202%3A11-18%2C%20Romans%202%3A11%2C%20only%20to%20name%20a%20few).%20Dismissing%20dispensationalism%2C%20adherents%20of%20Replacement%20Theology%20hold%20the%20view%20that%20God%E2%80%99s%20covenant%20to%20Jewish%20patriarchs%20(Abraham%2C%20Issac%2C%20and%20Jacob)%20were%20fulfilled%20in%20Christ%2C%20and%20the%20Church%20(meaning%2C%20all%20those%20who%20follow%20Christ%20and%20not%20a%20physical%20place%20called%20%E2%80%98Israel%E2%80%99)%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98new%20Israel%E2%80%99%2C%20according%20to%20II%20Corinthians%201%3A20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tragedy%20is%20that%20not%20many%20zealous%20Christian%20Zionists%20would%20be%20cognisant%20that%20Jesus%20himself%20was%20a%20Palestinian%20Jew%2C%20and%20more%20particularly%20a%20Palestinian%20Jewish%20refugee%20under%20the%20Roman%20Empire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Jesus%20were%20to%20be%20born%20today%2C%20he%20would%20have%20been%20born%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20side%20of%20the%20700-km%20wall%20built%20by%20Israel%2C%20passing%20through%20Bethlehem%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank.%20But%20for%20Christian%20Zionists%2C%20who%20present%20Jesus%20as%20a%20white%20man%20with%20blonde%20hair%2C%20facts%20matter%20little.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698568242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28232854%2FThe-Wire-59.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fhow-the-strident-support-of-evangelical-christians-to-israel-undermines-the-palestine-cause%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20Jesus%2C%20the%20most%20well-known%20Palestinian%20Jew%2C%20were%20to%20be%20born%20today%2C%20he%20would%20have%20been%20born%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20side%20of%20the%20700-km%20wall%20built%20by%20Israel%2C%20passing%20through%20Bethlehem%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank.%20But%20for%20Christian%20Zionists%2C%20who%20present%20Jesus%20as%20a%20white%20man%20with%20blonde%20hair%2C%20facts%20matter%20little.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fhow-the-strident-support-of-evangelical-christians-to-israel-undermines-the-palestine-cause%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Man%20Pretending%20to%20Be%20a%20Govt%20Officer%20Amasses%20Funds%20Worth%20Over%20Rs%204%20Crore%2C%20Arrested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144110%2Fajin-k-s-bOoEVNhRX_k-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0Gujarat%20Police%20has%20arrested%20an%20executive%20engineer%2C%20albeit%20a%20fake%20one%2C%20who%20flaunted%20his%20government%20credentials%20and%20embezzled%20roughly%20Rs%204.15%20crore%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctribal%20welfare%E2%80%9D.%20He%20gathered%20the%20money%20for%20more%20than%2093%20tribal%20welfare%20schemes.%20He%20had%20also%20opened%20up%20his%20government%20office%20in%20Chhota%20Udepur%20district%20of%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20Kiran%20Patel%20and%20Mayank%20Tiwari%20have%20been%20caught%20claiming%20to%20be%20top%20men%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(PMO).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Sandip%20Rajput%20confidently%20introduced%20himself%20as%20an%20executive%20engineer%20and%20claimed%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20Gujarat%20government%E2%80%99s%20irrigation%20department.%20He%20set%20up%20his%20base%20in%20Bodeli%2C%20in%20Chhota%20Udepur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20set%20up%20a%20fake%20office%20too%20on%20July%2021%2C%202021%2C%20and%20put%20a%20nameplate%20that%20described%20him%20%E2%80%98Executive%20Engineer%2C%20Irrigation%20Project%20Division%2C%20Bodeli%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajput%20also%20forged%20documents%2C%20signatures%20and%20other%20documents%20to%20portray%20himself%20as%20a%20government%20official.%20He%20acquired%2093%20government%20projects%20and%20received%20funds%20accumulating%20over%20Rs%204.15%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20complaint%20was%20registered%20by%20Javed%20Maknojiya%2C%20working%20as%20a%20junior%20clerk%20in%20the%20administrative%20office%20of%20the%20district%20collectorate.%20As%20per%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20when%20district%20collector%20(DC)%20Sachin%20Kumar%20convened%20a%20meeting%20on%20October%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20applications%20requesting%20for%20Rs%203.78%20crores%20for%2012%20border%20village%20and%20lift%20irrigation%20projects%20were%20discussed%2C%20when%20officials%20realised%20that%20no%20office%20of%20the%20executive%20engineer%20existed%20in%20Bodeli.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20investigation%20was%20launched%2C%20the%20DC%20sought%20details%20of%20the%20projects%20run%20by%20the%20Bodeli%20%E2%80%98office%E2%80%99%20and%20found%20that%20Rajput%20had%20received%20Rs%204.15%20crores%20since%202021%2C%20after%20which%20he%20and%20his%20associate%20Abu%20Bakr%20Saiyed%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Gujarat%20has%20witnessed%20several%20fraud%20cases%20where%20the%20accused%20impersonate%20government%20officials%20including%20those%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(CMO).%20One%20of%20these%20cases%20involved%20conman%20Kiran%20Patel%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20top%20director%20handling%20strategies%20and%20campaigns%20in%20the%20PMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatel%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Ahmedabad%20City%20Detection%20of%20Crime%20Branch%20(DCB)%20in%20April%20after%20the%20Gujarat%20Police%20took%20his%20custody%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20police%20arrested%20many%20others%20including%20Viraj%20Patel%2C%20Nikunj%20Patel%20and%20Lavkush%20Patel%2C%20who%20claimed%20to%20be%20officials%20of%20the%20CMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Ffake-feast-on-in-gujarat-yet-another-sarkari-fake-caught%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2F%5C%22%3EVibes%20of%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698566927000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20144110%2Fajin-k-s-bOoEVNhRX_k-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgujarat-man-pretending-to-be-a-govt-officer-amasses-funds-worth-over-rs-4-crore-arrested%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Gujarat%20has%20witnessed%20several%20fraud%20cases%20where%20the%20accused%20impersonate%20government%20officials%20including%20those%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20chief%