ID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-diwali-nears-what-s-taking-the-sheen-off-sivakasi-s-firecracker-sales-123102900320_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Firecracker%20ban%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Karnataka%20government%20not%20granting%20license%20for%20the%20sale%20are%20among%20several%20reasons%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-diwali-nears-what-s-taking-the-sheen-off-sivakasi-s-firecracker-sales-123102900320_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fas-diwali-nears-what-s-taking-the-sheen-off-sivakasi-s-firecracker-sales-123102900320_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fas-diwali-nears-what-s-taking-the-sheen-off-sivakasi-s-firecracker-sales-123102900320_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20Mention%20of%20Grabbing%20Neck%20in%20the%20FIR'%3A%20Gorakhpur%20Court%20Grants%20Bail%20to%20Rights%20Activists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29120519%2FF9idtFragAARMh-.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20local%20court%20in%20Gorakhpur%20on%20Saturday%20(October%2028)%20%E2%80%93%20while%20granting%20bail%20to%20activists%20and%20journalists%20accused%20of%20assaulting%20officials%20during%20a%20demonstration%20on%20land%20rights%20for%20Dalits%20%E2%80%93%20pointed%20to%20a%20major%20inconsistency%20in%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20the%20case%20by%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20inconsistency%20relates%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20attack%20alleged%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20raising%20questions%20on%20the%20merit%20of%20the%20charge%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%20being%20slapped%20against%20several%20activists%20and%20journalists%2C%20including%2079-year-old%20retired%20Indian%20Police%20Services%20officer-turned-human%20rights%20defender%20S.R.%20Darapuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20sessions%20judge%20Ashok%20Kumar%20granted%20bail%20to%20the%20three%20YouTube%20journalists%20and%20six%20other%20activists%20who%20had%20been%20arrested%20after%20they%20covered%20the%20October%2010%20demonstration%20organised%20by%20a%20local%20Ambedkarite%20outfit%2C%20Ambedkar%20Jan%20Morcha.%20The%20activists%20and%20journalists%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Dalit%2C%20were%20arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20unlawful%20assembly%2C%20vandalising%20official%20property%2C%20and%20abusing%2C%20threatening%20and%20assaulting%20the%20staff%20inside%20the%20divisional%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%20premises%20where%20the%20demonstration%20was%20held.%20Even%20though%20the%20demonstration%20concluded%20peacefully%2C%20they%20were%20booked%20for%20rioting%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%20and%20causing%20damage%20to%20public%20property%2C%20and%20other%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20more%20serious%20charges%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20which%20ensured%20they%20would%20not%20be%20liable%20for%20bail%20from%20a%20chief%20judicial%20magistrate%20court%20and%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20some%20days%20in%20jail%20before%20applying%20in%20a%20sessions%20court%2C%20were%20added%20to%20the%20FIR%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20attempt%20to%20murder%20charge%20was%20later%20added%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20medical%20report%20of%20the%20complainant%20Rajesh%20Kumar%20Sharma%2C%20a%20low-rung%20staff%20at%20the%20divisional%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office.%20The%20medical%20report%20mentioned%20that%20he%20had%20injuries%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20October%2011%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20peaceful%20protest%2C%20Sharma%20accused%20the%20protestors%20of%20indulging%20in%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Edhakka%20mukki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pushing%20and%20shoving)%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20staff%20after%20they%20asked%20them%20to%20clear%20the%20premises%2C%20citing%20prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20144.%20The%20FIR%20accuses%20the%20protestors%20of%20abusing%20the%20officials%2C%20obstructing%20them%2C%20tearing%20government%20documents%20inside%20the%20office%20and%20damaging%20flower%20pots%20on%20the%20premises%20by%20kicking%20them.%20They%20were%20also%20accused%20of%20threatening%20to%20kill%20the%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20no%20overt%20mention%20of%20any%20direct%20attempt%20on%20his%20life%20or%20use%20of%20any%20weapon%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJudge%20Ashok%20Kumar%2C%20while%20granting%20bail%20to%20Manoj%20Kumar%20(Ghaziabad)%2C%20Santosh%20Kumar%20Ambesh%20(Delhi)%20and%20Ramesh%20Chandra%20(Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar)%2C%20takes%20note%20of%20the%20omission%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20attack%20in%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgorakhpur-ambedkar-jan-morcha-land-rights-crackdown%5C%22%3EIn%20Yogi%E2%80%99s%20Gorakhpur%2C%20an%20Ambedkarite%20Outfit%20Speaking%20for%20Land%20Rights%20Faces%20State%20Crackdown%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%20under%20CrPC%20161%20before%20the%20investigation%20officer%20recorded%20in%20the%20case%20diary%2C%20Sharma%20says%20that%20Shravan%20Kumar%20Nirala%2C%20the%20president%20of%20AJM%20and%20organiser%20of%20the%20demonstration%2C%20instigated%20others%20to%20attack%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20someone%20from%20behind%20me%20grabbed%20my%20neck%2C%20while%20Shravan%20Kumar%20Nirala%20grabbed%20my%20neck%20from%20the%20front.%20Working%20in%20collusion%2C%20they%20started%20strangling%20me%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20kill%20me%20and%20pushed%20me%20to%20the%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharma%20said%20in%20his%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20medical%20report%2C%20signed%20by%20a%20medical%20officer%20of%20the%20Gorakhpur%20district%20hospital%2C%20mentions%20two%20injuries.%20While%20one%20relates%20to%20his%20neck%2C%20the%20other%20was%20an%20injury%20to%20his%20shoulder.%20%E2%80%9COpinion%3A%20Injury%20no%201%20is%20refer%20to%20ENT%20surgeon%20for%20opinion.%20Injury%20no%202%20is%20quo%20Rt.%20Shoulder%20joint%20are%20seen%20simple%20(sic)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20medical%20report%20cited%20in%20the%20bail%20order%20seen%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20taking%20note%20of%20the%20statement%20and%20medical%20report%20of%20Sharma%2C%20Judge%20Ashok%20Kumar%20points%20out%2C%20though%20without%20comment%20on%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20case%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20complainant%20makes%20no%20mention%20of%20anyone%20grabbing%20his%20neck.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20mentioned%20this%20point%20while%20granting%20bail%20to%20the%20other%20activists%20and%20journalists%20arrested%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20including%20Nirala.%20Darapuri%2C%20who%20had%20attended%20the%20demonstration%20for%20just%20an%20hour%20as%20a%20special%20invitee%2C%20was%20also%20granted%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20kin%20and%20associates%20of%20the%20activists%20and%20journalists%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20have%20maintained%20that%20the%20charges%20against%20them%20are%20fabricated%20and%20that%20the%20demonstration%20had%20ended%20peacefully%20with%20the%20district%20magistrate%20receiving%20their%20memorandum%20in%20full%20public%20view%20under%20amicable%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20demonstration%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EDera%20dalo%2C%20Ghera%20dalo%20andolan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20%E2%80%93%20was%20held%20to%20demand%20one%20acre%20of%20land%20for%20each%20landless%20Dalit%2C%20OBC%20and%20Muslim%20family.%20It%20recorded%20a%20large%20attendance%20of%20rural%20Dalit%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20nine%20persons%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20while%20a%20French%20scholar%2C%20Heinold%20Valentine%20Jean%20Roger%2C%20in%20India%20to%20research%20poverty%2C%20was%20also%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20visiting%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20without%20a%20valid%20permit%20and%20violating%20the%20provisions%20of%20The%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%201946.%20He%20was%20at%20the%20demonstration%20filming%20the%20events%20for%20a%20project%20he%20was%20working%20on%20when%20the%20police%20apprehended%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20the%20case%20named%2013%20persons%20and%2010-15%20unknown%20persons.%20Among%20those%20identified%20were%20writer%20Siddharth%20Ramu%2C%20lawyer%20Jai%20Bhim%20Prakash%2C%20AJM%20office-bearer%20Rishi%20Kapoor%20Anand%2C%20independent%20journalist%20Neelam%20Baudh%2C%20and%20former%20Peace%20Party%20MLA%20Ayub%20Ansari.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698561947000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29120519%2FF9idtFragAARMh-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-mention-of-grabbing-neck-in-the-fir-gorakhpur-court-grants-bail-to-rights-activists%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20granted%20bail%20to%20activists%20and%20journalists%20accused%20of%20assaulting%20officials%20during%20a%20peaceful%20demonstration%20on%20land%20rights%20for%20Dalits%20held%20on%20October%2010.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fno-mention-of-grabbing-neck-in-the-fir-gorakhpur-court-grants-bail-to-rights-activists%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Liverpool%20striker's%20parents%20kidnapped%20in%20Colombia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698561660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F70x70%2Fskynews-luis-diaz-liverpool_6340101.jpg%3F20231029064943%22%2C%22originID%22%