Fem%3E%20and%20two%20more%20for%20appearances%20as%20an%20associate%20White%20House%20counsel%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3EThe%20West%20Wing%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerry%20writes%20book%20about%20addiction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Perry%20released%20his%20memoir%2C%20%3Cem%3EFriends%2C%20Lovers%2C%20and%20the%20Big%20Terrible%20Thing%3A%20A%20Memoir%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20about%20his%20battle%20with%20alcohol%20and%20addiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20spend%20more%20than%20half%20his%20life%20in%20rehab%20and%20treatment%20centres%2C%20detoxing%20more%20than%2065%20times%20and%20paying%20millions%20trying%20to%20get%20sober.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%C2%A0wrote%20about%C2%A0his%20near-death%20experience%20in%202018%2C%20when%20his%20colon%20burst.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerry%E2%80%99s%20early%20life%20and%20his%20big%20break%20on%20%3Cem%3EFriends%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201969%2C%20Perry%20grew%20up%20between%20Montreal%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20after%20his%20parents%20separated%20when%20he%20was%20a%20baby%2C%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELos%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerry%20first%20tried%20his%20hand%20at%20playing%20tennis%20and%20he%20was%20successful%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20but%20he%20left%20the%20sport%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20acting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20acting%20young%20and%20appeared%20in%20hits%20like%20%3Cem%3EBeverly%20Hills%2C%2090210%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EA%20Night%20in%20the%20Life%20of%20Jimmy%20Reardon%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0opposite%20actor%20River%20Phoenix.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20big%20break%20came%20on%20%3Cem%3EFriends%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20premiered%20in%201994%20and%20where%20he%20starred%20opposite%20Jennifer%20Aniston%2C%20Courteney%20Cox%2C%20Matt%20LeBlanc%2C%20Lisa%20Kudrow%20and%20David%20Schwimmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerry%20played%20the%20role%20of%20Chandler%20Bing%2C%20a%20character%C2%A0known%20for%20his