0a%20universal%20cancer%20screening%20solution%20and%20is%20globally%20relevant%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2Fcervicheck-screening-kit-1681741153.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221155%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20self-sampling%20kit%20can%20be%20used%20by%20women%20directly%20to%20collect%20their%20own%20samples%20at%20home.%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-315524%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22692%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20self-sampling%20kit%20can%20be%20used%20by%20women%20directly%20to%20collect%20their%20own%20samples%20at%20home.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315492%2Fvadodara-pragmatech-healthcare-solutions-cervicheck-kits-detect-cervical-cancer-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECervicheck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECervical%20cancer%2C%20if%20detected%20early%20and%20treated%20promptly%2C%20can%20be%20effectively%20cured.%20Typically%2C%20it%20takes%2015%20to%2020%20years%20for%20cervical%20cancer%20to%20develop%20in%20women%20with%20normal%20immune%20systems%2C%20whereas%20for%20women%20with%20compromised%20immune%20systems%2C%20like%20those%20with%20untreated%20HIV%20infection%2C%20the%20development%20time%20is%20shortened%20to%205%20to%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVadodara-based%20Anirban%20Palit%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Dr%20Sayantani%20Pramanik%20developed%20a%20device%20called%20Cervicheck%20that%20helps%20detect%20cervical%20cancer%20at%20home.%20The%20self-sampling%20kit%2C%20they%20claim%2C%20can%20be%20used%20by%20women%2C%20particularly%20those%20living%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20directly%20to%20collect%20their%20own%20samples%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20kit%20gives%20accurate%20results%2C%20and%20it%20can%20not%20only%20do%20the%20HPV%20(human%20papillomavirus)%20test%20but%20also%20allows%20the%20gynaecologist%20to%20further%20check%20if%20the%20lesions%20are%20at%20the%20treatable%20stage%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Anirban.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309718%2Fmumbai-resident-jayashree-ratan-saaisha-knits-free-prostheses-for-breast-cancer-survivors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaaisha%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMumbai%20resident%20Jayashree%20Ratan%20creates%20crocheted%20prostheses%20for%20breast%20cancer%20survivors.%20These%20prostheses%20are%20made%20from%20100%20percent%20mercerised%20cotton%20yarn%2C%20which%20is%20soft%20on%20the%20skin%20and%20does%20not%20cause%20allergies.%20It%20is%20hand%20washable%20and%20fits%20well%20into%20the%20mastectomy%20bra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20points%20out%20that%20some%20women%20have%20access%20to%20silicone%20breast%20prostheses%2C%20but%20most%20do%20not%20and%20are%20forced%20to%20stuff%20handkerchiefs%20and%20cotton%20balls%20in%20their%20bras%20to%20create%20an%20illusion%20of%20full%20breasts.%20This%20practice%20often%20leads%20to%20rashes%2C%20infections%20or%20painful%20skin%20abrasions.%20It%20was%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20help%20such%20women%20that%20she%20started%20making%20crocheted%20prostheses%20for%20breast%20cancer%20survivors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2Fjayshree-ratan-1675087334.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jayashree%20Ratan%20creates%20crocheted%20prostheses%20for%20breast%20cancer%20survivors.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2Fjayshree-ratan-1675