e%5D%20WHO%20is%20trying%20to%20gather%20information%20on%20the%20overall%20impact%20on%20civilians%20and%20healthcare%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20reports%20of%20bombardment%20near%20the%20Indonesia%20and%20Al%20Shifa%20hospitals%20were%20%E2%80%9Cgravely%20concerning%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20Volker%20T%C3%BCrk%2C%20also%20voiced%20the%20same%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmbulances%20and%20civil%20defence%20teams%20are%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20locate%20the%20injured%2C%20or%20the%20thousands%20of%20people%20estimated%20to%20be%20still%20under%20the%20rubble%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-in-a-gaza-hospital-no-power-lack-of-medicines-many-operations-happening-without-anesthesia%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20in%20a%20Gaza%20Hospital%2C%20No%20Power%2C%20Lack%20of%20Medicines%2C%20Many%20Operations%20Happening%20Without%20Anesthesia%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETurk%20added%20that%20the%20civilians%20were%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20receive%20updated%20information%20on%20where%20they%20could%20access%20humanitarian%20relief%20and%20where%20they%20may%20be%20in%20less%20danger.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20journalists%20can%20now%20no%20longer%20report%20on%20the%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Office%20for%20the%20Coordination%20of%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20(OCHA)%2C%20as%20many%20as%207%2C326%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%2C%20of%20which%2066%25%20were%20women%20and%20children%2C%20even%20since%20the%20violence%20started.%20The%20OCHA%20in%20its%20October%2027%20update%20also%20said%20more%20than%2018%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20one-third%20of%20the%20hospitals%20and%20two-third%20of%20the%20primary%20health%20care%20centres%20have%20been%20shut%20down%20in%20Gaza.%20This%20not%20only%20puts%20at%20risk%20the%20wounded%20individuals%20who%20need%20urgent%20treatment%20but%20also%20jeopardises%20the%20well-being%20of%201%2C000%20kidney%20failure%20patients%20who%20require%20regular%20dialysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20WHO%20office%20in%20Palestine%2C%2080%25%20of%20the%20dialysis%20facilities%20are%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20worst%20hit%2C%20and%20where%20Israel%20has%20issued%20evacuation%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%209%2C000%20cancer%20patients%20who%20require%20chemotherapy%20and%20other%20care%20are%20also%20left%20with%20almost%20no%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20130%20neonates%20who%20require%20incubation.%20The%20incubators%20need%20electricity%20to%20function%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20which%20means%20these%20children%20will%20die%20once%20power%20goes%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20also%20said%20there%20are%2050%2C000%20pregnant%20women%2C%20with%20an%20average%20of%20183%20births%20taking%20place%20every%20day.%20With%20healthcare%20getting%20hit%2C%20all%20these%20people%20are%20badly%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20October%2019%2C%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Rik%20Peeperkorn%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20immediate%20trauma%20injuries%20get%20attention%2C%20the%20people%20suffering%20from%20non-communicable%20diseases%20like%20cardiovascular%20ailments%2C%20diabetes%2C%20cancer%2C%20hypertension%2C%20don%E2%80%99t.%20Similarly%2C%20women%20who%20require%20emergency%20obstetric%20care%20need%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20office%20in%20Palestine%20reported%20that%20at%20the%20Shifa%20hospital%20%E2%80%93%20the%20biggest%20hospital%20of%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20the%20bed%20occupancy%20rate%20has%20reached%20171%25.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20hospital%20is%20treating%20nearly%20three%20times%20the%20patients%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3Evis%20%C3%A0%20vis%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eits%20bed%20capacity.%20The%20overall%20occupancy%20rate%20at%20seven%20major%20hospitals%20stands%20at%20about%20119%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20puts%20pressure%20on%20the%20staff%20to%20free%20up%20beds%20for%20new%20patients%2C%20risking%20patient%20safety%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20daily%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20reported%20that%20due%20to%20severe%20fuel%20shortages%2C%20six%20hospitals%20have%20already%20halted%20their%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20warned%20that%20the%20medical%20equipment%20was%20increasingly%20becoming%20non-functional%2C%20affecting%20diagnostic%20and%20treatment%20capacities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDrinking%20water%20has%20been%20a%20major%20concern%20because%20most%20of%20the%20available%20water%20used%20to%20come%20from%20the%20ground.%20It%20is%20heavily%20salty%20and%20therefore%20requires%20desalination.%20But%20the%20abject%20lack%20of%20fuel%20has%20led%20to%20near%20complete%20halt%20of%20desalination%20plant%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20last%20OCHA%20update%2C%20water%20consumption%20has%20gone%20down%20to%20less%20than%2092%25%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpre-hostilities%E2%80%9D%20days.%20It%20said%20most%20of%20the%2065%20sewage%20pumping%20stations%20were%20also%20shut%20due%20to%20no%20fuel%2C%20thus%20exposing%20people%20to%20a%20host%20of%20infections.%20And%2C%20therefore%2C%20the%20outbreak%20of%20large-scale%20epidemics%20was%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698502592000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F18001445%2F1617px-World_Health_Organisation_building_from_west.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fambulances-unable-to-reach-the-wounded-in-palestine-due-to-communication-blackout-who%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20major%20UN%20and%20other%20agencies%20involved%20in%20giving%20humanitaria