20Leave%20School%20but%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Leave%20Any%20Child%20Behind%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Porter%20in%20Odisha%20Teaches%20Kids%20for%20Free%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECh%20Nageshu%20Patro%2C%20from%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Ganjam%20district%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20quit%20school%20as%20his%20parents%20could%20not%20afford%20the%20fees.%20An%20avid%20reader%20and%20a%20passionate%20person%2C%20Nageshu%20was%20heartbroken%20and%20determined%20to%20change%20his%20fate.%20He%20started%20working%20on%20odd%20jobs%20at%20the%20age%20of%2016%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20a%20job%20in%20a%20factory%20in%20Surat%20and%20had%20to%20leave%20behind%20everything%20including%20my%20home%20and%20dreams.%20The%20job%20paid%20me%20Rs%201%2C500%20from%20which%20I%20would%20send%20some%20money%20home%20and%20use%20the%20rest%20for%20sustaining%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENageshu%20longed%20to%20be%20near%20home%20and%20spent%20a%20few%20more%20years%20working%20at%20a%20Hyderabad%20shopping%20mall%20before%20finally%20returning%20to%20his%20hometown.%20In%202011%2C%20his%20brother%20informed%20him%20of%20a%20job%20opening%20in%20the%20Indian%20Railways%2C%20where%20he%20landed%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F241986%2Fladakh-siachen-glacier-indian-army-jawans-bravery-porter-stanzin-padma-jeevan-raksha-padak-award-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20as%20a%20porter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20years%20of%20struggle%2C%20when%20I%20was%20able%20to%20have%20a%20stable%20job%20as%20a%20porter%2C%20I%20was%20sure%20I%20wanted%20to%20help%20people%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20even%20while%20working%20and%20supporting%20his%20family%2C%20Nageshu%20kept%20putting%20money%20aside%20for%20his%20future.%20And%20in%202020%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Nageshu%20was%20left%20without%20a%20job%20like%20mos