ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332872%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20kids%20at%20the%20camp%20participating%20in%20an%20event.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20summer%20camp%20took%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20reputed%20family%20and%20marrying%20into%20another%2C%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20good.%20Her%20father%2C%20K%20Narayan%20Iyengar%2C%20was%20the%20director%20of%20Archaeology%20at%20the%20Government%20Museum%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20while%20her%20husband%2C%20R%20B%20Iyengar%2C%20was%20a%20scientist%20and%20close%20associate%20of%20Professor%20C%20N%20R%20Rao.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20lived%20in%20Amsterdam%20where%20he%20researched%20and%20she%20was%20a%20yoga%20trainer.%20But%20when%20Sudha%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20MS%2C%20where%20the%20degenerative%20disorder%20of%20the%20nervous%20system%20would%20soon%20hamper%20her%20movements%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20move%20back%20to%20India%20where%20help%20would%20be%20more%20easily%20available%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20taught%20at%20the%20MES%20Kishore%20Kendra%20in%20Malleswaram%20but%20after%20a%20few%20years%2C%20as