%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FAED-20-768x402.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-252008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20the%20documentary%20%E2%80%98An%20Engineered%20Dream%E2%80%99.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20race%20to%20the%20top%2C%20mental%20health%20is%20often%20ignored.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20work%20of%20the%20police%20student%E2%80%99s%20cell%2C%20counsellors%20and%20teachers%20like%20Singh%20is%20crucial.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20may%20be%20life%20saving.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20student%E2%80%99s%20cell%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20over%2080%2C000%20students%20so%20far%2C%20according%20to%20Thakur.%20They%20interact%20with%20teachers%2C%20hostel%20wardens%2C%20PG%20owners%2C%20mess%20staff%20and%20Thakur%20himself%20spends%20many%20evenings%20at%20different%20hostels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20to%20bring%20a%20positive%20change.%20Now%2C%20students%20know%20that%20they%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20us.%20Hostel%20wardens%20and%20mess%20staff%20are%20the%20most%20important%20link%20for%20us.%20They%20can%20observe%20any%20small%20change%20in%20a%20child%2C%20and%20we%20ask%20them%20to%20report%20it%20to%20us%20immediately.%20Even%20what%20seems%20like%20a%20small%20problem%2C%20say%20of%20food%2C%20is%20resolved%20immediately.%20We%20also%20ask%20coaching%20classes%20to%20take%20extra%20lessons%20if%20a%20child%20tells%20us%20that%20he%20or%20she%20is%20unable%20to%20understand%20a%20concept%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Life%20is%20bigger%20than%20one%20exam%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkota3-1698068081.jpg%